soning%20for%20doing%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESweeney%20has%20been%20among%20Apple's%20most%20vocal%20critics%20and%20has%20gotten%20louder%20in%20recent%20months.%20For%20context%2C%20Apple%20was%20obliged%20to%20make%20a%20series%20of%20changes%20to%20its%20App%20Store%20in%20order%20to%20comply%20with%20Europe's%20new%20Digital%20Markets%20Act%20(DMA)%20before%20a%20March%206%20deadline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20law%20stipulated%20that%20the%20App%20Store%2C%20which%20charges%20a%2030%25%20commission%2C%20was%20an%20unfair%20%26quot%3Bgatekeeper%26quot%3B%20as%20it%20acted%20as%20the%20only%20digital%20store%20where%20apps%20can%20be%20bought%20from%20for%20iPhones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20Apple%20must%20now%20allow%20other%20app%20stores%20on%20its%20iPhones%20%E2%80%94%20much%20to%20its%20dismay.%20But%20it%20still%20has%20retained%20control%20over%20which%20app%20stores%20are%20allowed%20onto%20iOS%20and%20will%20still%20take%20a%2017%25%20cut%20on%20transactions%20made%20through%20those%20stores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESweeney%20labeled%20this%20new%20reality%20%26quot%3Bhot%20garbage%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTimSweeneyEpic%2Fstatus%2F1750589570880516402%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%20a%20post%20on%20X%20in%20January%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20also%20called%20Apple's%20efforts%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20DMA%20a%20%26quot%3Bhorror%20show.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20Sweeney's%20intense%20criticism%20of%20Apple's%20efforts%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20DMA%2C%20Epic%20had%20nonetheless%20applied%20for%20a%20developer%20account%20to%20create%20its%20own%20store%20on%20Apple's%20operating%20system.%20The%20company%20even%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FEpicNewsroom%2Fstatus%2F1758516979705557241%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20managed%20to%20get%20it%20approved%20last%20month%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20complaints%20and%20more%20were%20cited%20in%20a%20letter%20from%20Apple's%20App%20Store%20chief%20Phil%20Schiller%20to%20Epic%20Games%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epicgames.com%2Fsite%2Fen-US%2Fnews%2Fapple-terminated-epic-s-developer-account%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhich%20was%20posted%20on%20the%20developer's%20website%20this%20week%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchiller%20said%20Sweeney's%20%26quot%3Bcolorful%20criticism%26quot%3B%20matched%20with%20Epic%20Games'%20%26quot%3Bpast%20practice%20of%20intentionally%20violating%20contractual%20provisions%20with%20which%20it%20disagrees%2C%26quot%3B%20suggested%20that%20it%20did%20not%20intend%20to%20follow%20its%20App%20Store%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20follow-up%20legal%20letter%2C%20Apple%20said%20that%20it%20could%20not%20allow%20Epic%20Games%20to%20be%20part%20of%20its%20ecosystem%20due%20to%20its%20%26quot%3Bpast%20and%20current%20conduct.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epicgames.com%2Fsite%2Fen-US%2Fnews%2Fapple-terminated-epic-s-developer-account%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblog%20post%20published%20on%20Wednesday%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Epic%20confirmed%20that%20Apple%20had%20terminated%20its%20developer%20account%2C%20meaning%20it%20%26quot%3Bcannot%20develop%20the%20Epic%20Games%20Store%20for%20iOS.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20terminating%20Epic's%20developer%20account%2C%20Apple%20is%20taking%20out%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20potential%20competitors%20to%20the%20Apple%20App%20Store%2C%26quot%3B%20Epic%20noted%20in%20its%20blog.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20undermining%20our%20ability%20to%20be%20a%20viable%20competitor%20and%20they%20are%20showing%20other%20developers%20what%20happens%20when%20you%20try%20to%20compete%20with%20Apple%20or%20are%20critical%20of%20their%20unfair%20practices.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E'Inconvenient'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EApple's%20decision%20to%20evict%20Epic%2C%20partly%20due%20to%20its%20public%20criticism%20of%20the%20company%2C%20has%20made%20some%20areas%20of%20the%20tech%20industry%20very%20uneasy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPaul%20Graham%2C%20a%20cofounder%20of%20famed%20startup%20accelerator%20Y%20Combinator%2C%20was%20among%20those%20to%20call%20out%20Apple's%20actions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20won't%20want%20to%20think%20about%20Apple%20being%20evil.%20It%20would%20be%20so%20inconvenient%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20want%20to%20switch%20to%20Android.%20But%20I%20see%20ever%20more%20signs%20that%20power%20has%20corrupted%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGergely%20Orosz%2C%20who%20writes%20the%20Pragmatic%20Engineer%20newsletter%2C%20said%20that%20Apple%20can%20and%20will%20remove%20developers%20who%20dare%20criticize%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EDare%20criticize%20Apple%20and%20they%20can%20(and%2C%20sometimes%2C%20will!)%20remove%20you%20from%20their%20platform%20as%20a%20developer.%20They%20just%20did%20this%20w%20Epic!%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EI%20cannot%20remember%20even%20Microsoft%20being%20this%20much%20of%20a%20bully%20back%20in%20the%2090s.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EApple%20became%20the%20very%20thing%20they%20fought%20against%20in%201984.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EShameful.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FqAweYCpqZo%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FqAweYCpqZo%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Gergely%20Orosz%20(%40GergelyOrosz)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FGergelyOrosz%2Fstatus%2F1765439068966412591%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%206%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EApple's%20decision%20has%20also%20captured%20the%20attention%20of%20European%20lawmakers%2C%20who%20have%20demanded%20the%20iPhone-maker%20provide%20it%20with%20%26q