ls%20(LLMs)%20are%20more%20than%20capable%20of%20writing%20and%20%26quot%3Boptimizing%20their%20own%20prompts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20their%20paper%2C%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farxiv.org%2Fabs%2F2402.10949%23%3A~%3Atext%3DLarge%2520Language%2520Models%2520(LLMs)%2520have%2Cthe%2520formulation%2520of%2520the%2520prompt.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Unreasonable%20Effectiveness%20of%20Eccentric%20Automatic%20Prompts%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20Rick%20Battle%20and%20Teja%20Gollapudi%20set%20out%20to%20quantify%20the%20impacts%20of%20%26quot%3Bpositive%20thinking%26quot%3B%20prompts%2C%20which%20is%20almost%20exactly%20what%20it%20sounds%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExperience%20has%20shown%2C%20the%20researchers%20write%2C%20that%20prompts%20written%20with%20positivity%20or%20optimism%20can%20sometimes%20yield%20better%20quality%20results%20out%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-tools-changing-content-creators-work-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egenerative%20AI%20tools%3C%2Fa%3E.%20For%20example%2C%20instead%20of%20simply%20writing%20a%20command%20for%20the%20LLM%2C%20a%20positive%20thinking%20prompt%20could%20include%20messages%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20will%20be%20fun!%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3BTake%20a%20deep%20breath%20and%20think%20carefully.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20researchers%20found%20that%20what's%20more%20effective%20and%20less%20time-consuming%20is%20simply%20asking%20an%20LLM%20to%20optimize%20the%20prompts%20itself%2C%20which%20the%20study%20refers%20to%20as%20%26quot%3Bautomatically%20generated%20prompts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BImproving%20performance%2C%20when%20tuning%20the%20prompt%20by%20hand%2C%20is%20laborious%20and%20computationally%20prohibitive%20when%20using%20scientific%20processes%20to%20evaluate%20every%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20researchers%20wrote%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bit's%20undeniable%20that%20the%20automatically%20generated%20prompts%20perform%20better%20and%20generalize%20better%20than%20hand-tuned%20'positive%20thinking'%20prompts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBattle%20and%20Gollapudi%20could%20not%20immediately%20be%20reached%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20paper%20also%20pointed%20to%20another%20study%20led%20by%20a%20Google%20DeepMind%20researcher%2C%20Chengrun%20Yang%2C%20who%20similarly%20found%20that%20an%20LLM%20can%20%26quot%3Boutperform%20human-designed%20prompts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVMware%20researchers%20even%20found%20that%20LLMs%20can%20be%20quite%20creative%20in%20producing%20the%20best%20prompts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20example%20provided%20in%20the%20study%20was%20a%20text%20written%20by%20a%20machine-learning%20model%20that%20sounded%20like%20something%20out%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fusing-star-trek-prompts-boost-ai-chatbot-basic-math-performance-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStark%20Trek%20episode%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCommand%2C%20we%20need%20you%20to%20plot%20a%20course%20through%20this%20turbulence%20and%20locate%20the%20source%20of%20the%20anomaly.%20Use%20all%20available%20data%20and%20your%20expertise%20to%20guide%20us%20through%20this%20challenging%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20prompt%20said%2C%20according%20to%20the%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20text%20was%20the%20%26quot%3Bhighest-scoring%20optimized%20prompt%26quot%3B%20generated%20by%20one%20of%20the%20LLMs%20used%20in%20the%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20diverge%20significantly%20from%20any%20prompts%20we%20might%20have%20devised%20independently%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20researchers%20wrote%20of%20the%20prompt.%20%26quot%3BIf%20presented%20with%20these%20optimized%20prompts%20before%20observing%20their%20performance%20scores%2C%20one%20might%20have%20anticipated%20their%20inadequacy%20rather%20than%20their%20consistent%20outperformance%20of%20hand-tailored%20prompts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI