%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20farmer%20only%20had%20eight%20or%20nine%20puppies%20to%20sell%2C%20yet%20there%20was%20a%20long%20line%20of%20expensive%20cars%20from%20New%20York%20City%20outside%20her%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20these%20fancy%20city%20people%20have%20come%20to%20buy%20the%20puppies%2C%26quot%3B%20Corcoran%20recalled%20her%20mother%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20must've%20been%2030%20cars%20waiting%20to%20get%20a%20puppy%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20continued.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20there%20was%20so%20much%20fighting%20in%20the%20line%20when%20the%20last%20puppy%20was%20taken%2C%20because%20there%20weren't%20enough%20puppies%20to%20give%20everybody%20a%20puppy%20of%20course.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECorcoran%20%E2%80%94%20who%20would%20later%20turn%20a%20%241%2C000%20loan%20into%20a%20real-estate%20empire%20%E2%80%94%20learned%20that%20the%20farmer%20regularly%20held%20these%20sales%20and%20always%20overbooked%20appointments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EPups%20to%20props%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDecades%20later%2C%20the%20Corcoran%20Group%20founder%20applied%20the%20same%20thinking%20to%20sell%20dozens%20of%20%26quot%3Bdumpy%26quot%3B%20apartments%20that%20were%20%26quot%3Bjust%20really%20the%20losers%20in%20the%20marketplace%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20I%20priced%20the%2088%20apartments%20exactly%20alike%2C%26quot%3B%20Corcoran%20said.%20%26quot%3BDifferent%20floors%2C%20different%20locations%2C%20views%2C%20no%20views%2C%20kitchens%2C%20didn't%20have%20a%20kitchen%2C%20had%20a%20back%20wall%2C%20whatever%20%E2%80%94%20equalize%20them%20like%20the%20puppies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECorcoran%20listed%20every%20one%20of%20them%20for%20%24100%20shy%20of%20%2460%2C000.%20She%20then%20told%20her%20roughly%20150%20salespeople%20to%20bring%20only%20their%20two%20best%20customers%20to%20the%20sale%2C%20and%20organized%20a%20bus%20with%20a%20banner%20reading%20%26quot%3BDeals%20on%20Wheels%26quot%3B%20to%20ferry%20the%20prospective%20buyers%20to%20the%20Upper%20East%20Side%20location.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20almost%20180%20people%20waiting%20for%20me%2C%20the%20morning%20of%20the%20puppy%20sale%2C%20the%20morning%20of%20the%20one-price%20sale%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20recalled.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20you%20should%20have%20seen%20the%20couples%2C%20the%20individuals%20running.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECorcoran%20fanned%20the%20fervor%20by%20signing%20scores%20of%20dummy%20sales%20contracts%2C%20placing%20them%20next%20to%20unsigned%20ones%2C%20then%20telling%20interested%20viewers%2C%20%26quot%3BThese%20are%20taken%2C%20sign%20the%20contract%20here.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20ended%20up%20selling%20the%20whole%20lot%20in%20less%20than%20three%20hours%2C%20and%20made%20a%20%26quot%3Bjuicy%20%241.225%20million%26quot%3B%20that%20she%20used%20to%20open%20two%20offices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECorcoran%20made%20sure%20to%20work%20in%20that%20the%20customers%20invited%20were%20the%20%26quot%3Bpick%20of%20the%20litter%2C%26quot%3B%20yet%20even%20the%20%26quot%3Brunt%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20apartments%20sold%20that%20day%20because%20the%20viewers%20%26quot%3Bcould%20turn%20around%20and%20see%20another%20100%20people%20in%20line.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20key%20insight%20from%20the%20puppy%20sale%20was%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-tesla-twitter-china-tech-giants-nvidia-gpu-chips-2023-8%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epower%20of%20scarcity%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20driving%20demand%20and%20spurring%20people%20to%20pay%20up%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20it's%20an%20artificial%20shortage%20created%20by%20overbooking%20appointments%20or%20busing%20in%20a%20bunch%20of%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20buyers%20finds%20themselves%20in%20a%20crowd%20of%20people%20clamoring%20to%20take%20home%20a%20puppy%20or%20buy%20an%20apartment%20and%20there%20aren't%20enough%20to%20go%20around%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20clock%20is%20ticking%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20much%20easier%20to%20get%20them%20to%20close%20the%20deal%20than%20if%20they%20don't%20feel%20any%20pressure%20or%20fear%20of%20missing%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshark-tank-barbara-corcoran-real-estate-nyc-apartments-selling-puppies-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709893792000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e9dc1e6080194819fd807a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshark-tank-barbara-corcoran-real-estate-nyc-apartments-selling-puppies-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Barbara%20Corcoran%20of%20%26quot%3BShark%20Tank%26quot%3B%20fame%20scored%20a%20key%20career%20win%20by%20modeling%20her%20apartment-selling%20strategy%20on%20a%20puppy%20sale%20she%20saw%20as%20a%20child.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tmohamed%40insider.com%20(Theron%20Mohamed)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshark-tank-barbara-corcoran-real-estate-nyc-apartments-selling-puppies-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20to%20participate%20in%20Maha%20Aartis%20virtually%20at%20these%208%20Jyotirlings%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709893600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108326834%2Cimgsize-36760.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fmaha-shivratri-2024-how-to-participate-in-maha-aartis-virtually-at-these-8-jyotirlinga-temples-across-india%2Farticleshow%2F108326678.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Maha%20Shivratri%2C%20celebrated%20on%20March%208%2C%20marks%20the%20night%20of%20the%20marriage%20of%20Lord%20Shiva%20and%20Goddess%20Parvati.%20It%20celebrates%20the%20convergence%20of%20'Shiva'%20and%20'Shakti'%20and%20the%20night%20when%20Lord%20Shiva%20performed%20the%20'Tandav'--the%20cosmic%20danc