ientificTemperStatementWithSignatories.pdf%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERead%20the%20full%20declaration%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EExecutive%20Summary%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0There%20is%20an%20urgent%20need%20for%20a%20renewed%20commitment%20to%20evidence-based%20reasoning%2C%20critical%20thinking%20and%20a%20scientific%20approach%20in%20India%2C%20especially%20amidst%20growing%20socio-political%20movements%20that%20challenge%20a%20scientific%20temper%20and%20universal%20knowledge%20production%20based%20on%20commonly%20agreed%20methods%20and%20understanding.%20Given%20the%20changes%20in%20society%20and%20technology%20since%20the%20earlier%20declarations%20on%20scientific%20temper%20in%201981%20and%202011%2C%20we%20emphasise%20the%20importance%20of%20embracing%20natural%20and%20social%20sciences%2C%20humanities%2C%20and%20the%20rational%20experiences%20of%20ordinary%20people%20in%20the%20common%20endeavour%20to%20combat%20the%20post-truth%20culture%2C%20the%20intentional%20promotion%20of%20ignorance%2C%20and%20diminishing%20trust%20in%20science%20exacerbated%20by%20misuse%20of%20technology.%20We%20call%20for%20action%20across%20three%20fronts%3A%20the%20State%E2%80%99s%20role%2C%20the%20involvement%20of%20scientific%20and%20academic%20institutions%2C%20and%20combating%20the%20undermining%20of%20science%20by%20the%20State%2C%20the%20erosion%20of%20academic%20freedom%2C%20and%20the%20spread%20of%20pseudo-science%20and%20unscientific%20beliefs.%20We%20urge%20scientists%2C%20intellectuals%2C%20and%20other%20like-minded%20individuals%20to%20support%20evidence-based%20thinking%20and%20policy-making%20and%20to%20uphold%20constitutional%20values%20to%20foster%20a%20scientific%20temper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIntroduction%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0Since%20the%20Coonoor%20Statement%20on%20Scientific%20Temper%20in%201981%20and%20the%20Palampur%20Declaration%20in%202011%2C%20there%20have%20been%20significant%20socio-political%20changes%20in%20India%20and%20around%20the%20world.%20Briefly%2C%20these%20earlier%20statements%20had%20emphasised%20the%20importance%20of%20fostering%20a%20scientific%20attitude%20among%20the%20people%20for%20development%20and%20social%20advancement.%20Over%20time%2C%20movements%20promoting%20scientific%20temper%20in%20India%20have%20also%20evolved%20in%20accordance%20with%20changing%20public%20perceptions%20of%20science%20and%20technology%20(S%26amp%3BT).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20new%20challenges%20have%20emerged%20in%20India%20and%20elsewhere%20in%20the%20world%20in%20the%20form%20of%20strong%20socio-political%20movements%2C%20backed%20by%20the%20State%20power%2C%20that%20seek%20to%20oppose%20any%20scientific%20approach%2C%20evidence-based%20reasoning%20or%2C%20indeed%2C%20any%20perspective%20that%20acknowledges%20universal%20scientific%20knowledge.%20Globally%2C%20a%20post-truth%20culture%20is%20spreading%2C%20marked%20by%20a%20deliberate%20spreading%20of%20ignorance%20and%20an%20anti-intellectual%20atmosphere%2C%20along%20with%20a%20diminishing%20trust%20in%20science.%20It%20is%20ironic%20that%20technology%2C%20part%20of%20the%20broad%20umbrella%20of%20science%2C%20is%20being%20harnessed%20to%20support%20these%20trends%20through%20social%20media%2C%20such%20that%20manufactured%20sentiment%2C%20prejudice%2C%20false%20narratives%2C%20baseless%20opinions%20and%20conspiracy%20theories%20gain%20acceptance%20as%20valid%20ways%20of%20thinking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgainst%20this%20background%2C%20the%20current%20situation%20requires%20a%20renewed%20commitment%20to%20robust%20evidence-based%20reasoning%2C%20drawing%20from%20accumulated%20knowledge%20in%20the%20natural%20and%20social%20sciences%2C%20and%20humanities%2C%20as%20well%20as%20from%20the%20know-how%20and%20rational%20experiences%20of%20working%20people.%20Such%20reasoning%20aligns%20with%20well-recognized%20methodologies%20of%20different%20disciplines%2C%20including%20emerging%20interdisciplinary%20research%2C%20applicable%20not%20only%20in%20academic%20environments%2C%20but%20also%20in%20public%20discourse%20and%20understanding.%20Both%20scientists%20and%20lay%20practitioners%20need%20to%20actively%20embrace%20and%20popularise%20these%20methods%20considering%20the%20new%20socio-political%20realities%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20contemporary%20statement%20on%20Scientific%20Temper%20has%20become%20essential%2C%20to%20address%20present%20challenges.%20This%20statement%20shall%20not%20undertake%20a%20critical%20review%20of%20the%20previous%20statements%20%2F%20declarations%20or%20debate%20their%20points.%20Instead%2C%20it%20acknowledges%20past%20debates%20and%20critiques%2C%20incorporating%20their%20essence%20into%20the%20current%20statement%2C%20recognizing%20the%20commonality%20of%20scientific%20disciplines%20and%20their%20methodologies.%20Rather%20than%20revisiting%20old%20debates%2C%20the%20focus%20here%20is%20on%20delineating%20the%20significant%20challenges%20faced%20in%20contemporary%20India%20for%20the%20constitutionally%20mandated%20task%20of%20promoting%20scientific%20temper%2C%20the%20spirit%20of%20inquiry%2C%20and%20humanism.%20Knowledge%20production%20and%20advancement%20through%20purposeful%20discovery%20and%20evidence-based%20reasoning%2C%20including%20thorough%20consideration%20of%20diverse%20opinions%2C%20is%20currently%20under%20severe%20threat%20both%20in%20academia%20and%20in%20society%20at%20large.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDangerous%20new%20theatre%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0As%20noted%20earlier%2C%20the%20arena%20for%20fostering%20scientific%20temper%20has%20evolved%20significantly%20in%20recent%20decades%2C%20becoming%20increasingly%20contested%2C%20including%20aggressive%20socio-cultural%20forces%20as%20well%20as%20governmental%20policies%20and%20administrative%20measures%20antagonistic%20to%20scientific%20temper.%20The%20current%20situation%20in%20India%20demands%20critical%20understanding%20and%20action%20on%20three%20interrelated%20fronts%3A%20the%20role%20of%20the%20State%20and%20polity%2C%20the%20character%20and%20function%20of%20scientific%20research%20and%20academic%20institutions%2C%20and%20malign%20influences%20in%20society%20and%20among%20the%20general%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArticle%2051A(h)%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20speaks%20of%20the%20duty%20of%20citizens%20to%20promote%20scientific%20temper.%20There%20is%20concern%20in%20some%20quarters%20that%20responsibilities%20of%20the%20State%20in%20this%20regard%20have%20not%20been%20adequately%20highlighted.%20While%20it%20might%20have%20been%20assumed%20that%20the%20State%E2%80%99s%20primary%20responsibility%20is%20implicit%20when%20citizens%20are%20called%20upon%20for%20certain%20duties%2C%20there%20is%20a%20need%20for%20a%20clearer%20delineation%20of%20the%20State%E2%80%99s%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENote%3A%20In%20the%20declaration%2C%20the%20terms%20%E2%80%98scientists%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98scientific%20institutions%E2%80%99%20are%20used%20as%20terms%20denoting%20all%20natural%20sciences%2C%20social%20sciences%20and%20humanities%20disciplines%2C%20and%20those%20others%20following%20an%20evidence-based%20path%20of%20knowledge%20production%20and%20understanding.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERole%20of%20the%20State%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0In%20the%20initial%20post-Independence%20decades%2C%20the%20Indian%20State%20placed%20significant%20trust%20in%20scientists%3Csup%3E1%3C%2Fsup%3E%C2%A0and%20scientific%20institutions.%20Development%20policies%20were%20evidence-driven%2C%20with%20research%20institutions%20and%20centres%20of%20excellence%20enjoying%20high%20priority%20and%20prestige%2C%20and%20enjoying%20substantial%20autonomy.%20Documents%20like%20the%20Industrial%20Policy%20Resolution%20and%20a%20unique%20Scientific%20Policy%20Resolution%20were%20foundational%20to%20planned%20development%2C%20guided%20by%20a%20multidisciplinary%20group%20of%20experts%20in%20the%20Planning%20Commission.%20Independent%20scientists%20and%20social%20scientists%2C%20both%20from%20India%20and%20abroad%2C%20were%20involved%20in%20policy-making%2C%20underlining%20the%20importance%20given%20to%20science%20and%20evidence-based%20policy-making.%20Notably%2C%20religion%20played%20a%20minimal%20role%20in%20state%20affairs%2C%20and%20secularism%2C%20defined%20as%20non-discrimination%20and%20equal%20respect%20for%20all%20religions%2C%20was%20practised.%20However%2C%20the%20evils%20of%20casteism%20and%20communalism%20have%20never%20been%20properly%20eliminated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20subsequent%20years%2C%20bureaucratism%2C%20elitism%2C%20and%20a%20techno-fix%20mentality%20crept%20into%20the%20system%2C%20creating%20something%20of%20a%20divide%20between%20scientists%20and%20the%20general%20public.%20Trust%20in%20scientific%20institutions%20also%20eroded%20as%20a%20perception%20grew%20that%20%E2%80%9Cestablishment%20science%E2%80%9D%20primarily%20served%20officialdom%20and%20corporate%20interests%2C%20rather%20than%20the%20public%20good%20as%20supported%20by%20verifiable%20data.%20During%20this%20period%2C%20academic%2C%20professional%2C%20and%20informed%20activist%20voices%20in%20civil%20society%20critiqued%20official%20narratives%2C%20influencing%20public%20opinion%20and%20contributing%20to%20critical%20thinking%20and%20evidence-based%20policymaking.%20While%20the%20State%20may%20not%20have%20proactively%20cultivated%20scientific%20temper%2C%20it%20engaged%20with%20and%20supported%20activities%20to%20popularise%20science%20among%20the%20wider%20public%20and%20children.%20The%20State%20also%20provided%20considerable%20space%20in%20governance%20and%20public%20discourse%20for%20non-official%20scientific%2C%20expert%2C%20and%20informed%20lay%20opinion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUndermining%20science%20and%20a%20scientific%20approach%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%20%C2%A0Presently%2C%20the%20State%20displays%20a%20stark%20departure%20from%20this%20earlier%20stance.%20Government%20and%20its%20various%20organs%20now%20actively%20oppose%20a%20scientific%20approach%2C%20independent%20or%20critical%20thinking%2C%20and%20evidence-based%20thinking%20and%20policy-making.%20This%20antagonistic%20stance%20is%20widely%20and%20persistently%20communicated%20to%20the%20public%20through%20various%20means%2C%20perpetuating%20such%20attitudes.%20State%20support%20for%20research%20and%20development%20(R%26amp%3BD)%2C%20already%20below%20comparable%20countries%20as%20a%20percentage%20of%20GDP%2C%20has%20hit%20historic%20lows%2C%20raising%20serious%20concerns%20about%20India%E2%80%99s%20future%20in%20the%20knowledge%20era.%20Domestic%20assembly%20by%20cheap%20labour%20is%20misrepresented%20as%20self-reliance%2C%20thus%20also%20underplaying%20the%20need%20for%20research%20and%20knowledge%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFunding%2C%20fellowships%2C%20and%20independent%20research%20face%20severe%20cuts%20in%20academic%20and%20research%20institutions%2C%20burdened%20by%20overpowering%20bureaucratic%20structures.%20Career%20advancement%20now%20favours%20adherence%20to%20dominant%20ideologies%2C%20sycophancy%2C%20and%20obedience%20to%20government%20directives%20over%20adherence%20to%20imperatives%20arising%20from%20domain%20expertise%20and%20research-based%20insights.%20Development%20data%20and%20India%E2%80%99s%20position%20in%20reputed%20international%20rankings%20are%20contested%20on%20spurious%20grounds.%20Similar%20data%20generated%20in%20India%2C%20even%20by%20government%20institutions%2C%20are%20rejected%20or%20manipulated%20to%20fit%20political%20narratives.%20On%20numerous%20issues%2C%20the%20government%20claims%20to%20lack%20data%2C%20but%20still%20proceeds%20with%20policy%20decisions.%20Open%20discussions%20in%20higher%20learning%20institutions%20are%20discouraged%2C%20hindering%20critical%20thinking%2C%20pluralism%2C%20and%20academic%20freedom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20image%20management%2C%20these%20tendencies%20undermine%20a%20scientific%20approach%20and%20evidence-based%20policymaking%2C%20demoralising%20the%20knowledge%20production%20community%20and%20fostering%20anti-intellectual%20attitudes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20State%20and%20allied%20social%20forces%20directly%20undermine%20science%20and%20its%20methods%20among%20the%20public.%20Unscientific%20claims%20by%20prominent%20figures%20in%20political%20circles%2C%20boasting%20of%20imaginary%20technological%20achievements%20and%20exaggerated%20ideas%20about%20ancient%20Indian%20knowledge%2C%20are%20used%20to%20build%20and%20support%20a%20hyper-nationalist%20narrative.%20These%20assertions%20lack%20evidence%2C%20relying%20on%20ambiguous%20mythological%20references%20and%20dubious%20interpretations%20of%20ancient%20texts%2C%20often%20draped%20in%20quasi-religious%20cover%20so%20as%20to%20suppress%20dissenting%20voices.%20Such%20fanciful%20and%20boastful%20claims%20undermine%20many%20actual%20substantial%20contributions%20of%20ancient%20India%20emanating%20from%20various%20cultural%20streams%20and%20covering%20intellectual%20as%20well%20as%20artisanal%20and%20technical%20accomplishments.%20Critics%20of%20such%20claims%20are%20readily%20branded%20as%20anti-national%20or%20westernised%2C%20questioning%20both%20history%20and%20science%2C%20and%20undermining%20the%20scientific%20method.%20Dissent%20and%20plurality%20of%20opinion%2C%20known%20to%20be%20enabling%20conditions%20for%20intellectual%20progress%2C%20are%20presently%20under%20threat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAssault%20on%20the%20education%20sector%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0It%20is%20disheartening%20to%20witness%20these%20trends%20now%20being%20introduced%20into%20the%20formal%20education%20system%2C%20potentially%20influencing%20an%20entire%20generation%20unless%20effectively%20countered.%20School%20textbooks%20and%20readings%20in%20higher%20education%20are%20undergoing%20revisions%20that%20promote%20the%20idea%20of%20the%20unquestioned%20superiority%20of%20knowledge%20in%20ancient%20India%2C%20while%20downplaying%20the%20role%20of%20other%20civilizations%20and%20their%20groundbreaking%20contributions.%20Whereas%20addressing%20Euro-centrism%20and%20acknowledging%20the%20contributions%20from%20ancient%20India%2C%20China%2C%20and%20other%20%E2%80%9Ceastern%E2%80%9D%20civilizations%20is%20essential%2C%20denying%20the%20emergence%20of%20modern%20science%20and%20technology%20and%20the%20industrial%20revolution%2C%20and%20the%20factors%20leading%20to%20it%2C%20is%20not%20only%20untruthful%20but%20also%20misleading.%20The%20giant%20strides%20of%20modern%20science%20and%20technology%20cannot%20be%20undermined%20or%20replaced%20by%20fictional%20narratives%2C%20as%20seen%20in%20revised%20school%20textbooks%20of%20agencies%20at%20the%20Centre%20and%20in%20various%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20revised%20textbooks%20also%20omit%20chapters%20on%20crucial%20historical%2C%20societal%2C%20economic%2C%20and%20ecological%20issues%20in%20India.%20In%20an%20examination-oriented%20system%20not%20fostering%20critical%20thinking%2C%20this%20leaves%20students%20ill-prepared%20for%20higher%20studies%20or%20research%20and%20for%20their%20roles%20as%20informed%20citizens%20contributing%20to%20national%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20higher%20education%2C%20mandatory%20courses%20on%20%E2%80%9Ctraditional%20knowledge%20systems%E2%80%9D%20are%20being%20introduced%2C%20presenting%20a-historical%20and%20distorted%20accounts%20of%20knowledge%20in%20ancient%20India.%20These%20courses%20exclusively%20glorify%20the%20Vedic-Sanskritic%20tradition%2C%20neglecting%20other%20cultural%20streams%20in%20ancient%20India%20and%20completely%20disregarding%20the%20significant%20generation%20of%20new%20knowledge%20in%20mediaeval%20India%2C%20out%20of%20prejudice%20against%20particular%20religious%20and%20cultural%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Estreams.%20This%20deliberate%20slant%20aims%20to%20erase%20or%20rewrite%20historical%20evidence%20and%20obstruct%20critical%20thinking%2C%20leaving%20students%20and%20citizens%20vulnerable%20to%20bias%20and%20instilling%20a%20distorted%20view%20of%20syncretic%20Indian%20traditions%20and%20multicultural%20reality.%20In%20the%20long%20run%2C%20this%20will%20result%20in%20incalculable%20damage%20to%20the%20progress%20of%20Indian%20science%20and%20to%20social%20harmony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESocietal%20attack%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0In%20recent%20decades%2C%20India%20has%20witnessed%20the%20growth%20of%20socio-religious%20orthodoxy%2C%20traditionalism%2C%20and%20revivalism%2C%20fueled%20by%20majoritarian%20socio-political%20forces.%20Traditional%20religious%20practices%2C%20festivals%2C%20and%20communal%20forms%20of%20organisation%20have%20proliferated.%20Numerous%20%E2%80%9CGodmen%E2%80%9D%20have%20emerged%20with%20substantial%20resources%2C%20sizable%20followings%2C%20and%20at%20times%2C%20significant%20political%20backing.%20These%20cults%2C%20despite%20projecting%20high-thinking%20spiritualism%2C%20have%20propagated%20superstitions%2C%20pseudo-scientific%20beliefs%2C%20and%20socio-religious%20orthodoxy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20social%20forces%20aligned%20with%20the%20ruling%20establishment%20and%20supported%20by%20the%20State%2C%20disseminate%20pseudo-science%20and%20a%20belief%20in%20mythology%20as%20history.%20False%20narratives%20are%20being%20used%20to%20construct%20a%20unitary%20majoritarian%20religion%20and%20culture%2C%20contrary%20to%20the%20diverse%20religious%20beliefs%20even%20among%20the%20majority%20community.%20False%20and%20unscientific%20narratives%2C%20such%20as%20vegetarianism%20as%20a%20dominant%20%E2%80%9Ctraditional%E2%80%9D%20practice%2C%20are%20being%20promoted%2C%20contradicting%20scientific%20surveys%20conducted%20by%20official%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20COVID%20pandemic%2C%20superstitions%20and%20pseudo-scientific%20notions%20related%20to%20health%20were%20actively%20promoted%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20endorsing%20%E2%80%9Ctraditional%E2%80%9D%20or%20ancient%20Indian%20health%20systems%20while%20implicitly%20or%20explicitly%20criticising%20modern%20medicine.%20Highly%20placed%20authorities%20encouraged%20practices%20like%20lighting%20lamps%20and%20clanging%20utensils%20to%20ward%20off%20the%20virus%2C%20with%20social%20media%20amplifying%20purported%20%E2%80%9Cproof%E2%80%9D%20of%20efficacy%2C%20such%20as%20recordings%20of%20%E2%80%9Ccosmic%20vibrations%E2%80%9D%20by%20NASA.%20Other%20pseudo-scientific%20claims%20are%20similarly%20backed%20by%20false%20evidence%20supposedly%20coming%20from%20reputed%20scientific%20agencies.%20Artificial%20creation%20of%20long-lost%20legendary%20ancient%20rivers%20is%20being%20undertaken%20to%20perpetuate%20mythology.%20All%20these%20exploit%20the%20enduring%20respect%20common%20people%20hold%20for%20science%20and%20its%20truth%20value.%20The%20forces%20of%20unreason%20seek%20to%20sow%20confusion%20regarding%20evidence%20and%20scientific%20methods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESocial%20media%20and%20digital%20technologies%20play%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20the%20State-backed%20dissemination%20of%20unscientific%20and%20anti-scientific%20views%2C%20pseudo-science%2C%20false%20narratives%2C%20and%20conspiracy%20theories%20aimed%20at%20undermining%20a%20scientific%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20closing%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20address%20the%20idea%20that%20%E2%80%9Cother%20worldly%E2%80%9D%20religious%20beliefs%20pose%20the%20only%20or%20major%20obstacle%20to%20fostering%20a%20scientific%20temper%20in%20India.%20Faith%20poses%20many%20challenges%20which%20science%20or%20rationalism%20may%20not%20always%20be%20able%20to%20tackle%2C%20insofar%20as%20faith%20itself%20may%20be%20defined%20or%20perceived%20as%20belonging%20to%20a%20non-physical%20domain.%20Freedom%20of%20religion%20or%20Individual%20faith%20may%20indeed%20be%20accorded%20due%20recognition.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20discriminatory%20practices%20or%20those%20that%20impinge%20on%20others%E2%80%99%20rights%20or%20affect%20public%20order%2C%20must%20be%20opposed%2C%20and%20their%20irrational%20basis%20explained.%20Obscurantism%20persists%20due%20to%20ongoing%20weaknesses%20in%20society%20itself%2C%20highlighting%20larger%20battles%20that%20need%20to%20be%20fought%2C%20of%20which%20the%20present%20one%20may%20be%20just%20a%20part.%20Given%20the%20organised%20challenges%20to%20a%20scientific%20approach%20discussed%20earlier%2C%20a%20more%20focused%20and%20targeted%20strategy%20is%20required%20for%20the%20campaign%20to%20promote%20or%20strengthen%20a%20scientific%20temper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDeclaration%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0We%20scientists%20and%20intellectuals%20across%20disciplines%2C%20activists%20and%20all%20individuals%20passionate%20about%20spreading%20a%20scientific%20temper%2C%20acknowledge%20that%20the%20struggle%20to%20promote%20a%20scientific%20temper%20is%20wide-ranging%20and%20embraces%20many%20dimensions.%20Yet%20we%20also%20understand%20that%2C%20given%20the%20grave%20threats%20posed%20in%20the%20current%20context%2C%20the%20major%20challenge%20in%20this%20period%20is%20to%20combat%20and%20roll%20back%20these%20threats.%20We%20realise%20the%20imminent%20danger%20posed%20by%20organised%20multi-pronged%20attacks%20to%20undermine%20a%20scientific%20attitude%20among%20the%20populace.%20Such%20attacks%20not%20only%20disseminate%20pseudo-science%2C%20blind%20faith%2C%20and%20unreason%20but%20also%20promote%20obscurantism%2C%20communitarian%20prejudices%2C%20and%20discrimination%2C%20striking%20at%20the%20core%20of%20a%20humanist%20approach.%20False%20narratives%2C%20unfounded%20opinions%2C%20and%20a%20cloak%20of%20religiosity%20are%20wielded%20to%20instil%20adherence%20to%20a%20manufactured%2C%20homogenised%2C%20majoritarian%20idea%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EWe%2C%20the%20signatories%20of%20this%20declaration%2C%20re-attest%20the%20importance%20of%20working%20towards%20promotion%20of%20scientific%20temper%20in%20society.%20We%20recognise%20the%20grassroots%20work%20put%20in%20by%20people%E2%80%99s%20science%20movements%2C%20other%20like-minded%20organisations%20and%20dedicated%20individuals%2C%20and%20commit%20to%20support%20these%20and%20other%20similar%20efforts.%20We%20appeal%20to%20like-minded%20individuals%20in%20academia%20and%20research%20institutions%2C%20the%20bureaucracy%2C%20and%20the%20political%20class%20to%20take%20a%20stand%20upholding%20constitutional%20values.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709892548000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F08153736%2Frohan-makhecha-jw3GOzxiSkw-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-sciences%2Fgovernment-now-actively-opposes-a-scientific-approach%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWe%20appeal%20to%20like-minded%20individuals%20in%20academia%20and%20research%20institutions%2C%20the%20bureaucracy%2C%20and%20the%20political%20class%20to%20take%20a%20stand%20upholding%20constitutional%20values%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20All%20India%20People's%20Science%20Network%20has%20said%20in%20its%20declaration.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-sciences%2Fgovernment-now-actively-opposes-a-scientific-approach%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20quit%20my%20draining%20IT%20job%20and%20moved%20to%20South%20Korea%20to%20teach%20English.%20The%20language%20barrier%20is%20tough%2C%20but%20I'm%20much%20happier%20here.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20man%20hiking%20on%20a%20mountain%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e9da11ce7f1785b2e74e53%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAlex%20Brown%20has%20lived%20in%20Cheongju%2C%20South%20Korea%20for%20six%20months.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Alex%20Brown%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAlex%20Brown%2C%20a%20UK%20native%2C%20moved%20to%20South%20Korea%20to%20teach%20English%20after%20quitting%20his%20IT%20job%20in%202023.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBrown%20was%20hired%20for%20a%20one-year%20teaching%20contract%20where%20he%20earns%20%C2%A31%2C200%20a%20month%20and%20lives%20for%20free.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDespite%20language%20and%20navigation%20challenges%2C%20Brown%20enjoys%20his%20new%20job%20and%20life%20in%20South%20Korea.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fadventuretoeverycountry.com%2Fhomepage%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%20Alex%20Brown%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20a%2030-year-old%20from%20Hampshire%2C%20England%2C%20who%20moved%20to%20South%20Korea%20to%20teach%20English.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20used%20to%20work%20a%20draining%20and%20tough%20job%20as%20an%20IT%20specialist.%20In%202021%2C%20the%20job%20went%20remote%20because%20of%20COVID-19.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20few%20months%20of%20remote%20work%2C%20my%20company%20ordered%20everyone%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fforcing-workers-back-office-risks-talent-exodus-dell-amazon-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eback%20to%20the%20office%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20just%20couldn't%20bring%20myself%20to%20go%20back%20to%20a%20cubicle%20for%20a%20job%20I%20didn't%20love%2C%20so%20I%20quit%20without%20a%20game%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20discovered%20a%20love%20for%20traveling%20after%20going%20to%20Bali%2C%20Cambodia%2C%20India%2C%20Turkey%2C%20and%20many%20other%20places.%20I%20knew%20I%20wanted%20to%20find%20a%20way%20to%20travel%20full-time%20for%20the%20foreseeable%20future%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgovernment-tech-contractor-job-overseas-travel-pay-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ework%20abroad%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20researching%20and%20discovered%20programs%20where%20I%20could%20teach%20English%20in%20different%20countries.%20I%20found%20one%20program%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsurprising-differences-between-us-south-korea-expat-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESouth%20Korea%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20required%20you%20to%20be%20a%20citizen%20of%20a%20country%20where%20English%20was%20the%20primary%20language%2C%20hold%20a%20bachelor's%20degree%2C%20and%20be%20willing%20to%20adapt%20to%20Korean%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20applied%2C%20and%20a%20private%20academy%20hired%20me%20on%20a%20one-year%20contract%20to%20start%20in%20September%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20didn't%20know%20what%20to%20expect%20before%20I%20moved%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20never%20been%20to%20South%20Korea%2C%20but%20I%20had%20heard%20that%20it's%20a%20safe%20country%20and%20people%20there%20have%20a%20reputation%20for%20being%20respectful%20and%20polite.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20job%20is%20in%20Cheongju%2C%20a%20city%20known%20as%20the%20cultural%20center%20of%20South%20Korea.%20Cheongju%20has%20historical%20significance%20as%20the%20birthplace%20of%20Jikji%2C%20the%20oldest%20existing%20book%20printed%20by%20the%20world's%20first%20moveable%20metal%20type%20printing%20system%2C%20predating%20even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgutenbergs-apprentice-by-alix-christie-2015-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGutenberg's%20printing%20press%3C%2Fa%3E.%20My%20first%20impression%20of%20the%20city%20was%20that%20it%20seemed%20very%20calm%20and%20clean.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20arrived%2C%20I%20was%20picked%20up%20by%20the%20director%20of%20my%20school.%20He%20took%20me%20to%20the%20studio%20apartment%20I%20would%20stay%20in%20for%20the%20next%20year%2C%20which%20is%20free%20and%20included%20in%20my%20contract.%20With%20barely%20a