lenging%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOutside%20of%20my%20school%20environment%2C%20it's%20hard%20to%20find%20anyone%20who%20speaks%20English.%20I%20haven't%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Flearning%2Fhow-to-learn-korean-language-online-classes-apps-videos-books%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elearned%20a%20lot%20of%20Korean%3C%2Fa%3E%20yet%20and%20can%20only%20say%20a%20few%20words.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20rely%20heavily%20on%20translation%20apps%20like%20Papago%2C%20the%20local%20equivalent%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-app-for-traveling-the-world-google-translate-2018-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20Translate%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Sometimes%20these%20apps%20don't%20work%20well%20and%20provide%20me%20with%20funny%20translations%20that%20are%20inaccurate.%20I%20use%20a%20combination%20of%20broken%20translations%20and%20hand%20gestures%20to%20get%20my%20point%20across.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20don't%20miss%20a%20lot%20about%20living%20in%20the%20UK%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20miss%20my%20friends%20and%20family%20and%20watching%20my%20favorite%20football%20team%20play%20in%20the%20UK.%20Other%20than%20that%2C%20I%20don't%20miss%20living%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20UK%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmost-expensive-countries-to-live-in-2017-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20expensive%20place%20to%20live%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20it's%20even%20hard%20to%20travel%20within%20the%20country%20without%20a%20big%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI'm%20glad%20I%20picked%20South%20Korea%20to%20live%20for%20a%20year%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20experience%20here%20has%20been%20positive%20so%20far.%20It's%20a%20nice%2C%20calm%2C%20and%20quiet%20country%20that's%20mostly%20affordable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20goal%20is%20to%20save%20as%20much%20money%20as%20possible%20to%20travel%20around%20Latin%20America%20and%20the%20Caribbean%20with%20my%20girlfriend%20after%20my%20job%20ends%20in%20September.%20After%20that%2C%20I%20want%20to%20find%20a%20job%20where%20I%20can%20work%20remotely%20so%20I%20can%20travel%20whenever%20I'd%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20want%20to%20stop%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdigital-nomad-life-quit-cons-downsides-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebeing%20a%20nomad%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20I%20love%20seeing%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-to-south-korea-teach-english-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709892421000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e9de826080194819fd82f1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-to-south-korea-teach-english-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Alex%20Brown%20moved%20to%20South%20Korea%20instead%20of%20returning%20to%20the%20office.%20He%20says%20the%20cost%20of%20living%20is%20affordable%20and%20the%20people%20are%20friendly%20and%20kind.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Jen%20Glantz)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-to-south-korea-teach-english-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Meet%20Drone%20Didis%3A%20Women%20In%20Rural%20India%20Learning%20To%20Fly%20High%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWomen%20in%20rural%20India%20are%20learning%20to%20fly%20high%2C%20using%20state-of-the-art%20technology.%20That%20is%20what%20the%20socially%20transformative%20Namo%20Drone%20Didi%20program%20is%20all%20about.%20Namo%20Drone%20Didi%20is%20an%20ambitious%20program%20announced%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20to%20leapfrog%20women%20in%20rural%20India%20to%20fly%20drones%20and%20catapult%20them%20into%20empowerment%20and%20social%20change%20by%20providing%20livelihood%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpasana%20Varma%20travelled%20from%20Barabanki%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20to%20Hyderabad%2C%20leaving%20her%20three%20young%20children%20in%20the%20care%20of%20her%20mother-in-law%20and%20husband%2C%20to%20become%20a%20drone%20pilot.%20She%20is%20among%20a%20group%20of%20women%20from%20the%20remotest%20corners%20of%20rural%20India%20who%20were%20trained%20at%20Hyderabad's%20National%20Institute%20of%20Plant%20Health%20Management%20to%20become%20what%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20called%20Drone%20Didis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20only%20seen%20a%20drone%20in%20a%20marriage%20shoot%20earlier.%20I%20used%20to%20think%2C%20we%20can't%20do%20it.%20But%20when%20Drone%20Didi%20program%20came%2C%20we%20thought%20we%20could%20learn%20too.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20classroom%20sessions%20with%20drone%20models%20and%20outdoor%20sessions%20too%2C%20teaching%20how%20to%20fly%20and%20maneuver%20the%20drones.%20The%20excitement%20and%20energy%20are%20palpable%20as%20the%20teacher%20explains%20in%20Hindi%20and%20the%20women%20talk%20about%20rotors%20and%20GPS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20part%20names%20are%20in%20English%20but%20he%20teaches%20in%20Hindi.%20Drone%20parts%2C%20how%20to%20roll%2C%20pitch%2C%20down%20and%20up%2C%20what%20GPS%20does%2C%20propeller%20and%20motor%2C%20what%20is%20the%20body%2C%20what%20parts%20are%20there%2C%20and%20how%20to%20know%20where%20the%20drone%20is.%20If%20men%20can%20do%20it%2C%20so%20can%20women.%20I%20we%20can%20look%20after%20our%20homes%2C%20large%20families%2C%20why%20not%20this%3F%20If%20we%20have%20the%20desire%20to%20learn%2C%20why%20not%3F%20What%20is%20it%20that%20women%20cannot%20do%3F%26quot%3B%20Upasana%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFifteen%20thousand%20SHG%20women%20are%20being%20trained%20to%20become%20drone%20pilots.%20Each%20of%20them%20is%20to%20be%20given%20a%20drone%20worth%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20that%20they%20will%20use%20to%20spray%20pesticides%20and%20fertilisers.%20The%20technology%20would%20empower%20women%20to%20become%20self-reliant%2C%20improving%20their%20livelihood%20through%20employment%20generation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHimani%20Bishnoi%20from%20Moradabad%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20says%20she%20wants%20to%20thank%20the%20PM%20for%20this%20wonderful%20opportunity.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20not%20even%20ridden%20a%20bike%2C%20now%20I%20will%20be%20a%20drone%20pilot.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKamini%20Devi%20from%20Bihar%20says%20with%20three%20children%20at%20home%2C%20she%20never%20got%20a%20chance%20to%20step%20out%20of%20home.%20%26quot%3BBut%20now%20with%20this%20livelihood%20opportunity%2C%20I%20won't%20have%20to%20ask%20others%20for%20money.%20We%20can%20support%20ourselves.%20We%20get%20self-confidence.%20We%20are%20meeting%20people%20who%20encourage%20us.%20I%20am%20very%20happy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKamini%20says%20her%20social%20status%20in%20the%20village%20will%20improve.%20%26quot%3BFarmers'%20time%20will%20be%20saved.%20Our%20income%20will%20increase.%20We%20are%20getting%20new%20tech%20to%20the%20village.%20It%20is%20a%20big%20thing%20to%20come%20from%20a%20village%20here%20to%20learn%20all%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoni%20has%20come%20with%20her%20breastfeeding%20seven-month-old%20baby%2C%20from%20Meerut%20to%20Hyderabad%2C%20to%20get%20the%20training%20needed%20to%20become%20a%20drone%20pilot%20and%20earn%20her%20certificate.%20Her%20husband%20manages%20the%20baby%20while%20she%20is%20attending%20the%20classes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20felt%20it%20would%20help%20increase%20our%20income.%20We%20can%20do%20more%20work%20with%20drones%2C%20so%20wanted%20to%20learn.%20The%20way%20they%20are%20teaching%2C%20I%20feel%20confident%20that%20we%20can%20do%20it.%20When%20we%20go%20back%20and%20tell%20people%2C%20they%20will%20get%20us%20to%20do%20the%20work.%20Will%20go%20village%20to%20village%20for%20this.%20Our%20income%20will%20also%20increase.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScientists%20point%20out%20that%20targeting%20and%20remote%20spraying%20using%20drones%20would%20minimize%20harmful%20health%20effects%20and%20also%20reduce%20costs%20for%20the%20farmer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Vidhu%20KP%2C%20joint%20director%20of%20the%20National%20Institute%20of%20Plant%20Health%20Management%2C%20says%20it%20may%20help%20reduce%20the%20excessive%20use%20of%20pesticides%20and%20fertilisers%20as%20it%20is%20a%20method%20of%20targeted%20use%20of%20the%20chemicals.%20%26quot%3BThe%20direct%20exposure%20to%20the%20chemicals%20will%20decrease.%20The%20push%20will%20also%20be%20for%20nano%20fertilizers.%20Both%20the%20cost%20and%20subsidy%20component%20for%20fertilizers%20are%20expected%20to%20come%20down%20deploying%20this%20technology%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWomen%20aged%2018%20to%2056%2C%20with%20a%20minimum%2010th%20class%20qualification%2C%20earn%20a%2010-year%20pilot%20license%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20training%20that%20teaches%20them%20to%20repair%2C%20maintain%2C%20simulate%20and%20finally%20fly%20the%20drones%20and%20ride%20their%20dreams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarut%20Drones%20is%20one%20of%20the%20Hyderabad-based%20firms%20that%20was%20asked%20to%20give%20demonstrations%20of%20drone%20technology%20and%20its%20use%20in%20multiple%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20big%20interest%20and%20enthusiasm.%20Many%20women%20came%20forward%20to%20learn%20the%20technology.%20Now%20that%20the%20government%20has%20facilitated%20the%20training%20of%20the%20SHG%20women%20to%20become%20drone%20pilots%2C%20as%20many%20as%20400%20women%20aged%2030%20to%2055%20have%20been%20trained%20by%20us%20so%20far%20from%20UP%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Prem%20Kumar%2C%20founder%20of%20Marut%20Drones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20roped%20in%20fertiliser%20PSUs%2C%20like%20IFFKO%20and%20KRIBHCO%20(in%20Uttarakhand%20an