y-outbreak%2Famp_articleshow%2F108325747.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fparrot-fever-outbreak-claims-lives-of-5-in-europe-what-is-this-new-deadly-outbreak%2Famp_articleshow%2F108325747.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIt%20Is%20Not%20Right%20At%20All%26quot%3B%3A%20Gill's%20Father%20Unhappy%20With%20India%20Star's%20New%20Role%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EShubman%20Gill's%20first%20coach%20and%20father%2C%20Lakhwinder%2C%20says%20his%20son%20stepping%20out%20to%20the%20bowlers%20again%20has%20allowed%20him%20to%20get%20back%20among%20the%20runs%20in%20Test%20cricket%20though%20he%20doesn't%20agree%20with%20his%20decision%20to%20bat%20at%20number%20three.%20Pressure%20was%20mounting%20on%20Shubman%20following%20the%20conclusion%20of%20the%20series%20opener%20against%20England.%20He%20had%20gone%20without%20a%20fifty%20in%2012%20innings%20and%20was%20guilty%20of%20not%20playing%20his%20attacking%20game.%20Playing%20with%20hard%20hands%20made%20matter%20worse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20struck%20his%20maiden%20hundred%20in%20the%20second%20innings%20of%20Vizag%20Test%20to%20silence%20his%20critics.%20It%20was%20also%20his%20major%20knock%20since%20dropping%20himself%20down%20to%20number%20three%20from%20the%20opening%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20father%2C%20who%20watched%20Shubman%20get%20to%20his%20second%20hundred%20of%20the%20series%20with%20a%20slog%20sweep%20here%20on%20Friday%2C%20spoke%20about%20the%20reasons%20that%20helped%20the%20India%20batter%20arrest%20his%20slide%20in%20red%20ball%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStepping%20out%20has%20made%20a%20big%20difference%2C%20he%20had%20stopped%20doing%20that%20and%20that%20created%20pressure.%20Since%20his%20U-16%20days%2C%20he%20has%20been%20stepping%20out%20to%20the%20spinners%20and%20pacers%20as%20well%20to%20cut%20the%20movement%2C%26quot%3B%20Lakhwinder%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20moment%20you%20don't%20play%20your%20natural%20game%20you%20are%20in%20trouble.%20The%20whole%20game%20is%20about%20confidence%2C%20when%20you%20get%20one%20good%20innings%20you%20are%20back%20to%20your%20best.%20Since%20his%20U-16%20days%2C%20he%20used%20to%20make%20tons%20of%20runs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGill%20charged%20down%20the%20track%20to%20both%20spinners%20and%20pacers%20on%20Friday%20including%20against%20the%20great%20James%20Anderson.%20In%20the%20first%20hour%20of%20play%2C%20Gill%20was%20at%20his%20sublime%20best%20as%20he%20took%20two%20steps%20to%20hit%20Anderson%20down%20the%20ground%20for%20a%20six%20with%20dead%20straight%20bat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELakhwinder%20loves%20when%20his%20son%20plays%20the%20square%20cut%20and%20cover%20drive%2C%20and%2C%20both%20were%20on%20display%20at%20the%20HPCA%20Stadium%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHe%20should%20have%20continued%20to%20open%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELakhwinder%2C%20who%20continues%20to%20train%20with%20Shubman%20whenever%20he%20is%20home%20in%20Mohali%2C%20also%20doesn't%20agree%20with%20his%20son's%20decision%20to%20bat%20at%20three.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20should%20have%20continued%20to%20open.%20It%20is%20not%20right%20at%20all%20I%20feel.%20When%20you%20sit%20in%20dressing%20room%20for%20longer%2C%20the%20pressure%20tense%20to%20increase.%20Number%203%20is%20not%20opening%20neither%20it%20is%20a%20middle-order%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPlus%20his%20game%20his%20not%20like%20that%2C%20it%20suits%20the%20likes%20of%20Cheteshwar%20Pujara%20who%20has%20a%20defensive%20game.%20When%20the%20ball%20is%20new%20you%20get%20more%20loose%20balls%2C%20when%20you%20come%20in%20after%205-7%20overs%2C%20the%20ball%20is%20still%20shiny%20and%20the%20bowler%20is%20also%20settled%20with%20his%20length.%26quot%3B%20However%2C%20he%20is%20a%20proud%20father%20and%20respects%20the%20decisions%20taken%20by%20his%20grown%20up%20son.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20inte