22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F08124450%2FMalviya-300x300.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F08124450%2FMalviya-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F08124450%2FMalviya-1024x1024.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F08124450%2FMalviya-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F08124450%2FMalviya.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-700748%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPhoto%3A%20Facebook%2FMahendrajeet%20Singh%20Malviya.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMalviya%2C%20who%20had%20been%20associated%20with%20the%20Congress%20since%20the%201990s%2C%20won%20the%20Bagidora%20assembly%20constituency%20in%20Banswara%20district%20for%20four%20consecutive%20times%20starting%20from%202008.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20Congress%20facing%20defeat%20in%20last%20year%E2%80%99s%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Malviya%20had%20won%20the%20Bagidora%20seat%20by%20over%2041%2C000%20votes%20while%20contesting%20on%20a%20Congress%20ticket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20hoping%20that%20by%20inducting%20Malviya%2C%20who%20holds%20substantial%20clout%20in%20the%20region%2C%20it%20will%20increase%20its%20chances%20of%20winning%20the%20Banswara%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency%20for%20a%20third%20consecutive%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20joining%20the%20BJP%2C%20Malviya%20resigned%20as%20an%20MLA%2C%20leaving%20the%20Bagidora%20seat%20vacant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMalviya%20has%20previously%20been%20a%20Congress%20MP%20from%20Banswara%20back%20in%201998.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%E2%80%99s%20poor%20performance%20in%20southern%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20ST%20seats%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20why%20did%20the%20BJP%20induct%20local%20strongman%20Malviya%2C%20a%20Congress%20politician%2C%20and%20field%20him%20from%20Banswara%20while%20denying%20a%20ticket%20to%20its%20incumbent%20MP%20Katara%2C%20whose%20work%20with%20the%20RSS-affiliated%20Vanvasi%20Kalyan%20Parishad%20spans%20decades%20in%20the%20region%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20answer%20can%20be%20gauged%20from%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20recent%20performance%20in%20the%20tribal-dominated%20Dungarpur%20and%20Banswara%20districts%2C%20where%20all%20nine%20assembly%20constituencies%20are%20reserved%20for%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20BJP%20emerged%20as%20the%20clear%20victor%20in%20the%20Rajasthan%20assembly%20elections%2C%20winning%20115%20of%20the%20200%20assembly%20constituencies%2C%20it%20could%20win%20only%20two%20of%20the%20nine%20seats%20in%20Dungarpur%20and%20Banswara.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20remaining%20seven%20constituencies%2C%20the%20Bharat%20Adivasi%20Party%20(BAP)%20won%20three%20seats%20while%20the%20Congress%20was%20victorious%20in%20four%20constituencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20BJP%20presently%20holding%20the%20Banswara%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%2C%20comprising%20eight%20of%20the%20nine%20assembly%20segments%20under%20Dungarpur%20and%20Banswara%20districts%2C%20its%20poor%20performance%20reflects%20the%20increasing%20clout%20of%20the%20BAP%2C%20which%20has%20changed%20the%20political%20equations%20in%20southern%20Rajasthan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERise%20of%20the%20BAP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BAP%20emerged%20as%20a%20dark%20horse%20in%20the%202023%20assembly%20elections%2C%20winning%20three%20seats%20in%20the%20Dungarpur%20and%20Banswara%20districts%20%E2%80%93%20not%20an%20easy%20feat%20to%20pull%20off%20in%20a%20state%20where%20the%20politics%20largely%20revolves%20around%20the%20Congress%20and%20BJP%2C%20with%20little%20space%20for%20any%20third%20political%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BAP%20had%20emerged%20as%20a%20splinter%20group%20from%20the%20Gujarat-based%20Bharatiya%20Tribal%20Party%20(BTP)%2C%20with%20most%20of%20the%20present%20BAP%20leaders%20being%20earlier%20associated%20with%20the%20BTP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20in%202018%2C%20the%20BTP%20had%20won%20two%20seats%20in%20the%20region.%20Subsequently%2C%20differences%20crept%20in%20between%20local%20tribal%20leaders%20in%20southern%20Rajasthan%20and%20the%20BTP%20leadership%2C%20which%20led%20to%20the%20BAP%E2%80%99s%20creation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BAP%20was%20created%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%202023%20assembly%20elections%20and%20enjoyed%20massive%20popular%20support%20in%20the%20tribal%20region.%20In%20its%20very%20first%20electoral%20foray%2C%20the%20BAP%20won%20three%20seats%20%E2%80%93%20Aaspur%2C%20Chorasi%20and%20Dhariyavad%20%E2%80%93%20emerging%20as%20a%20significant%20player%20in%20southern%20Rajasthan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frajasthan-congress-gehlot-sachin-pilot-bjp%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Badlega%20Raj%20ya%20Rivaaj%3F%E2%80%99%3A%20Rajasthan%20Votes%20for%20Change%20as%20BJP%20Scores%20Decisive%20Victory%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20was%20victorious%20in%20three%20seats%2C%20BAP%20candidates%20finished%20second%20in%20four%20constituencies%20%E2%80%93%20Bagidora%2C%20Dungarpur%2C%20Sagwara%20and%20Ghatol%20%E2%80%93and%20third%20in%20another%20four%20seats%20%E2%80%93%20Banswara%2C%20Garhi%2C%20Kushalgarh%20and%20Pratapgarh%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20tribal%20districts%20of%20Dungarpur%2C%20Banswara%20and%20Pratapgarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20that%20in%20many%20of%20these%20seats%2C%20the%20BAP%20polled%20more%20votes%20than%20either%20the%20Congress%20or%20the%20BJP%20reflected%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20growing%20support%20base%20in%20the%20area%2C%20banking%20on%20issues%20such%20as%20increased%20reservation%20for%20the%20tribal%20population%20and%20a%20separate%20state%20for%20the%20tribal%20Bhil%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBAP%20leaders%20say%20that%20they%20are%20all%20set%20to%20contest%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20planning%20to%20contest%20elections%20in%20around%20six-seven%20seats%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20including%20Banswara%2C%20Udaipur%2C%20Chittorgarh%20%5Band%5D%20Tonk-Sawai%20Madhopur.%20The%20BJP%20has%20inducted%20Malviya%20after%20seeing%20the%20power%20of%20the%20BAP.%20We%20are%20confident%20of%20winning%20the%20Banswara%20seat%20from%20where%20the%20BJP%20is%20fielding%20Malviya%2C%20Mohanlal%20Roat%2C%20national%20president%20of%20the%20BAP%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continued%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Congress%20is%20slowly%20shrinking%20in%20the%20tribal%20districts%20and%20the%20BAP%20is%20emerging%20as%20the%20main%20threat%20to%20the%20BJP.%20Our%20cadre%20is%202%20lakh%20strong%20and%20we%20have%20supporters%20in%20every%20village.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERoat%20added%20that%20the%20BAP%20is%20at%20present%20deciding%20on%20alliances%20with%20other%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECongress%E2%80%99s%20dilemma%20and%20alliance%20talks%20with%20BTP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20losing%20Malviya%20%E2%80%93%20its%20tallest%20leader%20in%20southern%20Rajasthan%20%E2%80%93%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20had%20fared%20well%20in%20the%20tribal%20districts%20of%20Banswara%20and%20Dungarpur%20in%20the%202023%20assembly%20election%20which%20it%20otherwise%20lost%2C%20is%20presently%20in%20a%20dilemma%20and%20is%20rethinking%20its%20strategy%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leaders%20have%20been%20scathing%20in%20slamming%20Malviya%20for%20joining%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20%5BMalviya%5D%20will%20not%20be%20accepted%20in%20the%20BJP.%20Our%20Congress%20workers%20had%20made%20him%20this%20big%20a%20leader%2C%20and%20he%20betrayed%20them.%20He%20was%20not%20the%20son%20of%20a%20king.%20He%20was%20the%20son%20of%20an%20Adivasi%2C%20who%20rose%20because%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%20became%20a%20minister%20and%20was%20given%20important%20departments%2C%E2%80%9D%20Govind%20Singh%20Dotasra%20recently%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F08125343%2FRajasthan-Congress-1024x768.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F08125343%2FRajasthan-Congress-1024x768.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F08125343%2FRajasthan-Congress-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F08125343%2FRajasthan-Congress.jpeg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-700750%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22630%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Rajasthan%20unit%20is%20in%20a%20dilemma%20after%20Malviya%E2%80%99s%20exit.%20File%20image.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40INCRajasthan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20workers%20will%20ensure%20that%20he%20loses%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20He%20was%20a%20leader%20because%20of%20Congress%20workers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMalviya%E2%80%99s%20departure%20has%20also%20made%20the%20Congress%20explore%20options%20of%20a%20possible%20alliance%20with%20the%20BAP%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20state%20Congress%20president%20Dotasra%20maintained%20that%20any%20decision%20on%20allying%20with%20other%20parties%20would%20be%20taken%20by%20the%20committee%20formed%20by%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20high%20command%20to%20decide%20on%20alliances%2C%20sources%20in%20the%20Rajasthan%20Congress%20confirmed%20that%20alliance%20talks%20are%20presently%20ongoing%20with%20the%20BAP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Congress%20leaders%20may%20be%20tight-lipped%20about%20any%20possible%20alliance%20with%20the%20BAP%2C%20sources%20said%20that%20sections%20within%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20are%20seriously%20considering%20a%20possible%20alliance%20with%20the%20BAP%2C%20as%20the%20Congress%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20lose%20out%20in%20a%20three-way%20contest%20involving%20itself%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20BAP%20in%20a%20region%20where%20the%20Congress%20had%20fared%20well%20in%20the%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20leaders%20said%20that%20the%20party%20is%20confident%20of%20winning%20the%20Banswara%20seat%20once%20again%20with%20the%20help%20of%20a%20popular%20tribal%20leader%20like%20Malviya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMahendrajeet%20Malviya%20was%20an%20MLA%20for%20four%20consecutive%20times.%20He%20has%20been%20an%20MP%20before%20and%20members%20of%20his%20family%20have%20been%20the%20zila%20%3Cem%3Epramukh%3C%2Fem%3E%20since%20the%20last%2025%20years.%20Congress%20had%20been%20losing%20elections%20but%20Malviya%20had%20been%20winning.%20Had%20the%20Congress%20been%20able%20to%20make%20someone%20win%20elections%2C%20it%20could%20have%20made%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20win%20from%20Amethi%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Rajasthan%20BJP%20spokesperson%20Laxmikant%20Bhardwaj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMalviya%20is%20a%20leader%20with%20public%20support%20and%20instead%20of%20him%20being%20a%20leader%20because%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%20it%20was%20the%20Congress%20which%20was%20present%20in%20the%20area%20because%20of%20his%20influence%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bhardwaj%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20Malviya%20quitting%20Congress%2C%20the%20party%20has%20been%20erased%20from%20the%20entire%20region.%20The%20BJP%20will%20benefit%20from%20Malviya%20joining%20the%20party%20and%20we%20are%20confident%20of%20winning%20the%20Banswara%20seat.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20back%20in%202014%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20won%20all%2025%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%20state%2C%20in%202019%2C%20the%20party%20was%20victorious%20in%2024%20seats%20while%20the%20Rashtriya%20Loktantrik%20Party%2C%20which%20was%20then%20its%20ally%20and%20a%20part%20of%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%2C%20had%20won%20the%20Nagaur%20parliamentary%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709890257000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F08123857%2FBAP2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fhow-an-adivasi-party-is-changing-political-equations-in-southern-rajasthans-tribal-districts%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Bharat%20Adivasi%20Party%20has%20increased%20its%20clout%20in%20the%20region%2C%20banking%20on%20issues%20such%20as%20increased%20reservation%20for%20the%20tribal%20population%20and%20a%20separate%20state%20for%20the%20tribal%20Bhil%20community.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fhow-an-adivasi-party-is-changing-political-equations-in-southern-rajasthans-tribal-districts%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM%20Surya%20Ghar%20Muft%20Bijli%20Yojana%3A%20FAQs%20on%20eligibility%20answered%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709890066000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108325023%2Cimgsize-1831214.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fpm-surya-ghar-muft-bijli-yojana-can-you-apply-faqs-on-eligibility-application-process-and-other-details-answered%2Farticleshow%2F108325068.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22PM%20Surya%20Ghar%20Muft%20Bijli%20Yojana%20is%20a%20government%20scheme%20that%20offers%20subsidies%20for%20solar%20panels%20to%20eligible%20individuals.%20The%20scheme%20requires%20Indian%20citizenship%2C%20suitable%20roof%20for%20solar%20panels%2