allenges%20faced%20by%20students%20in%20the%20high-pressure%20academic%20environment%20prevailing%20in%20coaching%20centres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20central%20government's%20guidelines%20and%20efforts%20by%20the%20district%20administration%20to%20provide%20counseling%20facilities%20and%20alleviate%20stress%20among%20coaching%20students%2C%20the%20grim%20reality%20persists.%20Last%20year's%20toll%20of%2026%20student%20suicides%20had%20already%20raised%20alarms%2C%20and%20the%20situation%20remains%20dire%20with%20half%20a%20dozen%20cases%20reported%20within%20the%20first%20three%20months%20of%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKota%20welcomes%20over%20two%20lakh%20students%20aspiring%20for%20competitive%20exams%20like%20JEE%20and%20NEET%20every%20year.%20The%20struggle%20for%20success%20is%20often%20accompanied%20by%20challenges%20that%20extend%20beyond%20academics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kota%20administration%2C%20in%20collaboration%20with%20stakeholders%20from%20the%20coaching%20industry%2C%20last%20year%20took%20a%20series%20of%20initiatives%20to%20address%20the%20alarming%20issue%20of%20student%20suicides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20step%20involved%20the%20installation%20of%20%26quot%3Bsuicide-proofing%26quot%3B%20fans%20in%20hostel%20rooms.%20These%20devices%20incorporate%20spring%20coils%2C%20activating%20a%20siren%20if%20an%20object%20weighing%20more%20than%2020%20kg%20is%20hung%20from%20them.%20Despite%20being%20proposed%20by%20the%20Kota%20Hostels'%20Association%20in%202017%2C%20it%20gained%20traction%20only%20recently%20when%20the%20district%20administration%20mandated%20its%20implementation%20in%20response%20to%20a%20surge%20in%20suicides%20in%20August%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20this%2C%20nets%20have%20been%20strategically%20placed%20in%20balconies%20and%20lobbies%20to%20prevent%20students%20from%20taking%20drastic%20steps.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ctable%3E%3Cthead%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Cth%20colspan%3D%5C%222%5C%22