r%20he%20earns%20gets%20exhausted%20in%20meeting%20my%20in-law%E2%80%99s%20expenses%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%2024-year-old%2C%20who%20works%20as%20a%20domestic%20help%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMeanwhile%2C%20my%20salary%20would%20be%20exhausted%20in%20meeting%20the%20household%20expenses.%20Living%20in%20Gurgaon%20is%20an%20expensive%20affair.%20It%20would%20cost%20me%20up%20to%20Rs%2010%2C000%20to%20Rs%2012%2C000%20per%20month%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20medical%20expenses.%20It%20was%20getting%20extremely%20difficult%20for%20us%20to%20manage%20daily%20expenses%2C%20let%20alone%20save%20anything%20for%20the%20future%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20bid%20to%20earn%20an%20additional%20income%2C%20Priya%20set%20up%20a%20small%20business%20to%20sell%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F313743%2Fchethan-shetty-quit-corporate-job-to-become-farmer-in-bellare-mangaluru-earns-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexotic%20fruits%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20nuts.%20Started%20in%20the%20condominium%20where%20she%20works%20as%20a%20domestic%20help%2C%20today%20she%20has%20managed%20to%20earn%20a%20strong%20customer%20base%20of%20250%20people%20in%20Gurugram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fwomens-day-2-1709877153.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%202022%2C%20Priya%20and%20her%20husband%20set%20up%20a%20small%20business%20to%20sell%20exotic%20fruits%20and%20nuts.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fwomens-day-2-1709877153.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fwomens-day-2-1709877153-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen