cer%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fdelhi%2Fpakode-walis-protest-from-lecture-hall-to-frying-pan-dr-ritu-singhs-fight-against-injustice%2Farticleshow%2F108278839.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Enoted%20that%20Singh%20had%20named%20the%20items%20on%20her%20menu%20as%20markers%20of%20protest%2C%20like%20%E2%80%98jumla%20pakoda%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98special%20recruitment%20drive%20pakoda%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98berozgari%20special%20chai%E2%80%99.%20%E2%80%9CI%20want%20the%20teachers%20and%20students%20to%20see%20the%20plight%20of%20Dalit%20academics%20and%20the%20systemic%20barriers%20they%20face%20even%20after%20graduating%20from%20the%20prestigious%20Delhi%20University%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20told%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20early%202018%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20famously%20said%20when%20asked%20about%20unemployment%20in%20an%20interview%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20someone%20opens%20a%C2%A0%3Cem%3Epakoda%3C%2Fem%3E%20shop%20in%20front%20of%20your%20office%2C%20does%20that%20not%20count%20at%20employment%3F%20The%20person%E2%80%99s%20daily%20earning%20of%20Rs%20200%20will%20never%20come%20into%20any%20books%20or%20accounts.%20The%20truth%20is%20massive%20people%20are%20being%20employed.%E2%80%9D%20Several%20experts%20have%20pointed%20out%20why%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20remarks%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fpakoda-employment-has-increased-poverty-over-the-last-eight-years%5C%22%3Ewere%20misguided%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709875374000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F08104508%2FGHze0T_W4AAD30u.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fex-du-teacher-protesting-caste-discrimination-termination-with-pakoda-stall-faces-police-case%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dr%20Ritu