g%20attempt%20to%20murder%20against%20a%20prominent%20Muslim%20cleric-politician%20for%20communal%20violence%20in%20Bareilly%20in%202010%20%E2%80%93%20has%20hailed%20chief%20minister%20Adityanath%20as%20a%20great%20example%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Creligious%20person%E2%80%9D%20holding%20a%20seat%20of%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20same%20order%2C%20the%20judge%20makes%20a%20string%20of%20controversial%20and%20debatable%20observations%20%E2%80%93%20from%20praising%20Adityanath%20for%20his%20religious%20background%20to%20blaming%20alleged%20%E2%80%9Cappeasement%E2%80%9D%20of%20a%20particular%20community%20by%20political%20parties%20for%20riots%20in%20the%20country%20and%20referring%20to%20his%20own%20record%20in%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20legal%20battle%20and%20threats%20received%20by%20him%20from%20Muslim%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20even%20said%20that%20a%20copy%20of%20his%20order%20should%20be%20sent%20to%20Adityanath%20so%20that%20the%20chief%20minister%20could%20take%20action%20against%20those%20senior%20police%20officers%20and%20officials%20who%20allegedly%20assisted%20the%20accused%20Muslim%20cleric%20Maulana%20Tauqeer%20Raza%20Khan%20and%20did%20not%20act%20as%20per%20law%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20the%20then%20government%20(UP%20was%20under%20the%20rule%20of%20the%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20at%20the%20time).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERavi%20Kumar%20Diwakar%2C%20additional%20district%20judge-fast%20track%20court%20in%20Bareilly%2C%20who%20passed%20the%20order%2C%20while%20serving%20as%20a%20judge%20in%20Varanasi%20in%202022%20had%20passed%20controversial%20directions%20regarding%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid.%20Diwakar%2C%20as%20civil%20judge%20senior%20division%2C%20had%20ordered%20the%20sealing%20of%20a%20portion%20of%20the%20Mughal-era%20mosque%20after%20Hindu%20plaintiffs%20claimed%20that%20a%20stone%20found%20in%20the%20ablution%20tank%20there%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cshivling%E2%80%9D.%20Judge%20Diwakar%20had%20given%20his%20nod%20to%20videography%20inside%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20by%20a%20court-appointed%20advocate%20commissioner%20on%20a%20petition%20filed%20by%20five%20Hindu%20plaintiffs%20demanding%20daily%20access%20to%20prayer%20to%20a%20%E2%80%98Maa%20Shringar%20Gauri%E2%80%99%20they%20claimed%20was%20located%20outside%20the%20western%20wall%20of%20the%20mosque.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20posted%20in%20Bareilly%2C%20Judge%20Diwakar%20on%20March%205%2C%20while%20hearing%20the%202010%20Bareilly%20riots%20case%2C%20added%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20name%20in%20the%20chargesheet%20and%20summoned%20him%20to%20appear%20before%20it%20on%20March%2011.%20The%20judge%20dubbed%20Khan%2C%20who%20is%20a%20prominent%20cleric%20of%20the%20Barelvi%20sect%20and%20president%20of%20the%20political%20party%20Ittehad-e-Millat%20Council%2C%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmain%20mastermind%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20riots%20that%20took%20place%20in%20Bareilly%20on%20March%202%2C%202010%20after%20a%20dispute%20broke%20out%20over%20the%20route%20of%20a%20Muslim%20religious%20procession.%20Several%20persons%20were%20injured%20and%20property%20damaged%20in%20the%20incident.%20A%20curfew%20had%20been%20imposed%20in%20the%20city%20for%20several%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20recording%20the%20statements%20of%20witnesses%2C%20the%20judge%20concluded%20that%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20speech%20to%20a%20gathering%20a%20Muslims%20had%20instigated%20the%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJudge%20Diwakar%2C%20who%20was%20posted%20to%20his%20present%20court%20in%20November%202023%2C%20started%20off%20by%20stating%20that%20if%20a%20religious%20person%20occupies%20a%20seat%20of%20power%2C%20it%20leads%20to%20good%20results.%20He%20cited%20the%20concept%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98philosopher%20king%E2%80%99%20propounded%20by%20ancient%20Greek%20philosopher%20Plato%20in%20his%20work%20%3Cem%3ERepublic%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Plato%20had%20said%20that%20there%20would%20be%20no%20end%20to%20suffering%20in%20the%20Greek%20city%20states%20until%20they%20had%20philosopher%20kings%2C%20said%20Diwakar%20in%20his%20order%20hearing%20the%20Bareilly%20riots%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJustice%20is%20the%20lifeblood%20of%20a%20king%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Diwakar%2C%20quickly%20adding%20that%20though%20in%20the%20present%20times%20the%20word%20%E2%80%98justice%E2%80%99%20was%20used%20in%20the%20legal%20sense%2C%20during%20the%20time%20of%20Plato%20it%20was%20used%20in%20the%20context%20of%20religion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTherefore%2C%20the%20head%20of%20power%20should%20be%20a%20religious%20person%2C%20because%20the%20life%20of%20a%20religious%20person%20is%20not%20one%20of%20enjoyment%20but%20of%20sacrifice%20and%20dedication.%20An%20example%20of%20this%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20times%20is%20the%20peethadeshwar%20of%20the%20great%20Siddhapeeth%20Gorakhnath%20Temple%2C%20mahant%20baba%20shri%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20ji%2C%20who%20is%20the%20current%20chief%20minister%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20has%20proven%20the%20above%20concept%20to%20be%20true%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Judge%20Diwakar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20however%2C%20if%20any%20religious%20person%20acts%20contrary%20to%20the%20aforementioned%2C%20such%20as%20provoking%20people%20of%20this%20community%2C%20then%20law%20and%20order%20gets%20disrupted%20and%20riots%20occur%2C%20said%20the%20judge.%20Diwakar%20said%20an%20example%20of%20this%20was%20Maulana%20Khan.%20The%20judge%20stressed%20that%20since%20Khan%20is%20a%20religious%20leader%20and%20belonged%20to%20the%20Ala%20Hazrat%2C%20the%20main%20dargah%20of%20Bareilly%2C%20which%20has%20great%20recognition%20in%20the%20Muslim%20society%2C%20and%20heads%20the%20IMC%2C%20he%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20influence%20in%20Muslim%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJudge%20Diwakar%20further%20remarked%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmain%20reason%20for%20riots%E2%80%9D%20in%20India%20was%20that%20%E2%80%9Cpolitical%20parties%20here%20are%20engaged%20in%20appeasement%20of%20a%20particular%20religion%E2%80%9D.%20Due%20to%20this%2C%20the%20morale%20of%20prominent%20people%20of%20that%20%E2%80%9Cparticular%20religion%E2%80%9D%20increases%20to%20the%20extent%20that%20they%20believe%20that%20even%20if%20they%20cause%20riots%2C%20no%20harm%20will%20fall%20upon%20them%20due%20to%20protection%20provided%20by%20power%2C%20said%20Diwakar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20then%20recalled%20his%20time%20in%20Varanasi%20and%20referred%20to%20the%20alleged%20threats%20he%20received%20following%20his%20orders%20in%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20matter.%20He%20said%20that%20even%20though%20he%20had%20filed%20an%20FIR%20after%20receiving%20a%2032-page%20threat%20from%20a%20Muslim%20outfit%2C%20nobody%20had%20been%20arrested%20till%20date.%20This%20caused%20his%20mother%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20Lucknow%2C%20and%20his%20younger%20brother%2C%20a%20civil%20judge%20in%20Shahjahanpur%2C%20to%20worry%20about%20his%20safety%2C%20said%20Diwakar%2C%20adding%20that%20an%20atmosphere%20of%20fear%20prevailed%20in%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20then%20referred%20to%20the%20alleged%20remarks%20by%20Khan%20against%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20even%20claimed%20that%20had%20UP%20not%20been%20ruled%20by%20Adityanath%2C%20Khan%20would%20have%20recently%20incited%20a%20riot%20in%20Bareilly.%20He%20was%20referring%20to%20the%20incident%20of%20stone-pelting%20that%20took%20place%20in%20Bareilly%20last%20month%20when%20people%20were%20returning%20home%20after%20participating%20in%20a%20jail-bharo%20protest%20organised%20by%20Khan%20against%20the%20decision%20of%20a%20court%20in%20Varanasi%20to%20hand%20over%20the%20basement%20of%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20to%20Hindus%20for%20prayer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJudge%20Diwakar%20then%20claimed%20that%20ever%20since%20he%20passed%20the%20verdict%20in%20the%20Gyanvapi%20case%2C%20the%20attitude%20of%20people%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Cparticular%20religion%E2%80%9D%20and%20officials%20towards%20him%20had%20become%20strange.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20seemed%20that%20I%20had%20committed%20some%20sin%20by%20giving%20the%20verdict%20in%20the%20Gyanvapi%20case%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20judge%2C%20stressing%20that%20he%20passed%20the%20order%20as%20per%20legal%20provisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegarding%20the%20Bareilly%20rioting%20case%2C%20the%20judge%2C%20while%20criticising%20the%20alleged%20inaction%20of%20the%20police%20and%20government%20officials%20in%20failing%20to%20include%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20name%20in%20the%20chargesheet%20despite%20there%20being%20sufficient%20evidence%20in%20the%20investigation%2C%20noted%20that%20in%20India%2C%20rarely%20has%20the%20mastermind%20of%20a%20riot%20been%20punished.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20Khan%20had%20been%20arrested%20he%20was%20not%20named%20in%20the%20chargesheet%20of%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiwakar%20is%20not%20the%20only%20judge%20linked%20to%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid-Kashi%20Vishwanath%20matter%20to%20stir%20a%20controversy.%20As%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fajaya-krishna-vishvesha-handed-gyanvapi-cellar-hindus-ombudsman-university-in-lucknow%5C%22%3Efirst%20reported%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20retired%20district%20judge%20of%20Varanasi%20Ajaya%20Kumar%20Vishvesha%20who%20had%20on%20January%2031%2C%20his%20last%20working%20day%2C%20controversially%20handed%20over%20the%20basement%20of%20the%20Gyanvapi%20mosque%20to%20Hindus%20for%20prayers%2C%20was%20recently%20appointed%20an%20ombudsman%20of%20a%20public%20university%20in%20Lucknow.%20Adityanath%2C%20by%20virtue%20of%20being%20chief%20minister%2C%20is%20the%20chairperson%20of%20the%20university.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709873057000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F08101344%2FFcWENqHaQAIDJ0v.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fex-gyanvapi-case-judge-hails-philosopher-king-adityanath-in-order-indicting-muslim-cleric%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Judge%20Ravi%20Kumar%20Diwakar%20called%20Adityanath%20a%20great%20example%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Creligious%20person%E2%80%9D%20holding%20a%20seat%20of%20power.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fex-gyanvapi-case-judge-hails-philosopher-king-adityanath-in-order-indicting-muslim-cleric%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Plane%20makes%20emergency%20landing%20after%20wheel%20falls%20off%20during%20takeoff%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709872283000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108316802%2Cimgsize-1673311.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Funited-airlines-plane-emergency-landing-after-boeing-jet-wheel-falls-off-during-takeoff%2Farticleshow%2F108316718.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108316718.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EA%20Boeing%20777%20jet%20made%20an%20emergency%20landing%20after%20a%20wheel%20fell%20off%2C%20damaging%20cars.%20Flight%20redirected%20to%20Los%20Angeles.%20United%20Airlines%20plane%20missing%20a%20wheel%20but%20landed%20safely.%20Boeing%20facing%20quality%20control%20issues%2C%20including%20grounding%20of%20Boeing%20737%20Max%209s.%20FAA%20instructs%20Boeing%20to%20improve%20quality%20control%20within%2090%20days.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20News%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Funited-airlines-plane-emergency-landing-after-boeing-jet-wheel-falls-off-during-takeoff%2Farticleshow%2F108316718.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Funited-airlines-plane-emergency-landing-after-boeing-jet-wheel-falls-off-during-takeoff%2Famp_articleshow%2F108316718.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Funited-airlines-plane-emergency-landing-after-boeing-jet-wheel-falls-off-during-takeoff%2Famp_articleshow%2F108316718.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20(Re)Marriage%20of%20Convenience%20Is%20in%20the%20Making%20in%20Odisha%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F08091041%2FGH6wRL5W4AAQK0I.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBhubaneswar%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20quite%20a%20game%2C%20politics.%20There%20are%20no%20permanent%20enemies%2C%20and%20no%20permanent%20friends%2C%20only%20permanent%20interests%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20William%20Clay.%20As%20if%20testifying%20to%20the%20truth%20of%20this%20statement%2C%20the%20Naveen%20Patnaik-led%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20(BJD)%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20currently%20the%20main%20opposition%20party%20in%20Odisha%2C%20seem%20set%20to%20revive%20their%20alliance%20that%20had%20collapsed%20ahead%20of%20the%202009%20general%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlliance%20talks%20gained%20momentum%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20one-day%20visit%20to%20the%20state%20on%20March%205%2C%20during%20which%20he%20was%20seen%20holding%20chief%20minister%20Naveen%20Patnaik%E2%80%99s%20hand%20and%20exchanging%20pleasantries%20with%20him.%20Things%20started%20moving%20at%20a%20fast%20pace%20the%20very%20next%20day%20when%20senior%20state%20BJP%20leaders%20were%20called%20to%20Delhi%20and%20BJD%20leaders%20went%20into%20a%20huddle%20at%20Naveen%20Niwas%2C%20the%20official%20residence%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%20who%20has%20been%20the%20president%20of%20the%20regional%20party%20since%20its%20birth%20in%201997.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReliable%20sources%20said%20that%20a%20formal%20announcement%20with%20regard%20to%20the%20alliance%20could%20be%20made%20in%20the%20next%20few%20days%2C%20most%20probably%20on%20March%2012%20when%20Union%20home%20minister%20and%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20right-hand%20man%20Amit%20Shah%20is%20likely%20to%20visit%20the%20state.%20%E2%80%9COnly%20the%20seat-sharing%20arrangement%20has%20to%20be%20finalised.%20The%20BJP%20wants%2013%20out%20of%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%2021%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20and%20at%20least%2054%20assembly%20seats.%20This%20may%20not%20be%20acceptable%20to%20the%20BJD.%20Then%20there%20is%20the%20issue%20of%20seat%20selection%2C%20which%20could%20turn%20out%20to%20be%20trickier%20than%20it%20seems.%20Once%20these%20things%20are%20sorted%20out%2C%20a%20formal%20announcement%20will%20be%20made%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20who%20did%20not%20wish%20to%20be%20identified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJD%20presently%20has%2012%20Lok%20Sabha%20members%20and%20accounts%20for%20112%20of%20the%20147%20seats%20in%20the%20state%20assembly.%20The%20BJP%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20holds%20eight%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20including%20all%20five%20in%20western%20Odisha%2C%20its%20traditional%20stronghold.%20With%2022%20seats%20in%20the%20state%20assembly%2C%20it%20also%20enjoys%20the%20honour%20of%20being%20the%20main%20opposition%20party%2C%20a%20title%20earlier%20held%20by%20the%20Congress%20which%20has%20now%20been%20reduced%20to%20just%20nine%20seats%20in%20the%20state%20assembly.%20The%20Congress%20holds%20just%20one%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20%E2%80%93%20Koraput%20%E2%80%93%20in%20southern%20Odisha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20alliance%20and%20seat-sharing%20issues%20being%20discussed%20at%20the%20highest%20level%2C%20state%20leaders%20of%20both%20parties%20are%20being%20extremely%20cautious%20in%20their%20reactions.%20Speaking%20to%20local%20TV%20channels%2C%20senior%20BJD%20leader%20and%20former%20minister%20Debi%20Prasad%20Mishra%20tried%20to%20side-step%20the%20issue%20of%20an%20alliance.%20However%2C%20asked%20repeatedly%20about%20it%20after%20the%20meeting%20at%20Naveen%20Niwas%2C%20he%20vaguely%20remarked%20that%20%E2%80%9Ceverything%20was%20discussed%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMixed%20emotions%20in%20the%20BJP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20BJP%20leaders%20have%20been%20more%20forthright%20while%20commenting%20on%20the%20issue.%20Former%20party%20MLA%20Pradeep%20Purohit%20not%20only%20admitted%20that%20the%20chances%20of%20a%20revival%20of%20the%20alliance%20between%20the%20two%20parties%20appeared%20bright%2C%20but%20also%20exuded%20confidence%20about%20the%20BJP%20gaining%20much%20more%20than%20the%20BJD%20from%20this.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20it%20happens%2C%20which%20seems%20almost%20certain%2C%20there%20will%20be%20a%20coalition%20government%20again%20and%20we%20will%20be%20back%20in%20power.%20Besides%2C%20it%20is%20almost%20certain%20that%20the%20BJP%20will%20win%20more%20assembly%20seats%20than%20it%20did%20in%202019.%20What%20is%20most%20important%20from%20our%20point%20of%20view%20is%20that%20all%20the%2021%20Lok%20Sabha%20MPs%20from%20the%20state%20will%20support%20the%20BJP-led%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Purohit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20not%20all%20leaders%20of%20the%20party%20share%20his%20optimism%20and%20enthusiasm.%20Mohan%20Majhi%2C%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20tribal%20face%20and%20its%20deputy%20leader%20in%20the%20state%20assembly%2C%20is%20apprehensive%20that%20the%20hard%20work%20the%20party%20cadre%20did%20in%20several%20constituencies%20for%20the%20last%20five%20years%20to%20strengthen%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20base%20may%20go%20waste.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20cannot%20be%20sure%20if%20we%20will%20get%20those%20seats.%20The%20truth%20is%20we%20have%20been%20working%20over%20time%20to%20strengthen%20our%20position%20across%20the%20state.%20The%20BJD%20was%20our%20main%20enemy%20but%20now%20the%20whole%20equation%20is%20going%20to%20change.%20Though%20the%20central%20leadership%E2%80%99s%20decision%20has%20to%20be%20respected%2C%20there%20is%20no%20denying%20the%20anger%20among%20our%20workers%20as%20we%20are%20going%20to%20join%20hands%20with%20the%20party%20which%20had%20ditched%20us%20in%202009%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Majhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMajhi%2C%20however%2C%20admitted%20that%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20central%20leadership%20has%20its%20own%20compulsions.%20%E2%80%9COur%20slogan%20this%20time%20is%20%3Cem%3Eabki%20baar%2C%20char%20sau%20paar%3C%2Fem%3E%20(let%E2%80%99s%20cross%20the%20400-seat%20mark%20this%20time).%20For%20this%20goal%20to%20be%20realised%2C%20we%20may%20have%20to%20make%20some%20compromises.%20We%20may%20need%20to%20revive%20old%20alliances%20and%20also%20win%20new%20allies.%20But%20it%20will%20be%20extremely%20difficult%20to%20convince%20the%20ordinary%20workers%20who%20have%20been%20working%20round%20the%20year%20for%20the%20growth%20of%20the%20party%20in%20the%20state%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20leader.%20Most%20BJP%20leaders%20in%20the%20state%2C%20though%20unwilling%20to%20go%20on%20record%20at%20this%20juncture%2C%20share%20Majhi%E2%80%99s%20concerns%20about%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20cadre%20rebellion%20in%20the%20state%20in%20the%20event%20of%20the%20BJD-BJP%20alliance%20being%20revived.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20alliance%20and%20a%20break%20up%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20denying%20that%20the%20BJD-BJP%20alliance%20that%20came%20into%20existence%20in%201998%2C%20just%20a%20year%20after%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20regional%20party%2C%20was%20a%20marriage%20of%20convenience%2C%20as%20there%20was%20no%20ideological%20match%20between%20the%20two%20parties.%20The%20BJD%2C%20being%20a%20fledgling%20party%2C%20found%20it%20politically%20wise%20to%20join%20hands%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20was%20on%20the%20upswing%20at%20the%20time.%20The%20fact%20that%20Atal%20Behari%20Vajpayee%2C%20whose%20liberal%20views%20made%20him%20acceptable%20across%20the%20political%20spectrum%2C%20was%20the%20top%20leader%20of%20the%20BJP%20made%20the%20decision%20of%20an%20alliance%20easier%20for%20the%20regional%20party%20which%20was%20named%20after%20Biju%20Patnaik%2C%20the%20father%20of%20Naveen%20and%20two-time%20chief%20minister%20of%20the%20state%20whose%20secular%20credentials%20were%20never%20in%20doubt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20important%20factor%20that%20dictated%20BJD%E2%80%99s%20choice%20of%20its%20ally%20was%20that%20it%20treated%20the%20Congress%20as%20its%20prime%20enemy%20right%20from%20the%20beginning.%20The%20BJD-BJP%20alliance%20also%20swept%20to%20power%20in%20Odisha%20in%202000%20on%20an%20anti-Congress%20plank.%20The%20coalition%20had%20then%20sought%20to%20expose%20the%20corruption%20and%20inefficiency%20of%20the%20incumbent%20Congress%20government%2C%20which%20had%20completely%20mismanaged%20the%20relief%20and%20rehabilitation%20work%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%201999%20super-cyclone%20which%20had%20devastated%20the%20entire%20coastal%20belt%20of%20Odisha%2C%20leaving%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20people%20dead%20and%20lakhs%20homeless.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20there%20could%20be%20no%20question%20of%20aligning%20with%20the%20Congress%2C%20and%20BJP%20became%20the%20ally%20of%20the%20regional%20party%20almost%20by%20default.%20The%20two-party%20coalition%20ran%20the%20state%20for%20nearly%20nine%20years%2C%20but%20the%20going%20was%20never%20completely%20smooth%20given%20their%20differences%20over%20a%20number%20of%20issues.%20Senior%20BJP%20leaders%20like%20former%20Union%20minister%20Jual%20Oram%20openly%20criticised%20the%20chief%20minister%20when%20the%20state%20government%20signed%20a%20memorandum%20of%20understanding%20with%20South%20Korean%20steel%20behemoth%20Pohang%20Steel%20Company%20(POSCO)%20for%20setting%20up%20a%2012%20million%20tonne%20capacity%20steel%20plant%20in%20Jagatsinghpur%20district%20and%20the%20company%20started%20eyeing%20iron%20ore%20reserves%20in%20Khandadhar%20which%20is%20part%20of%20Sundergarh%2C%20Oram%E2%80%99s%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20BJP%20leaders%20also%20detested%20Patnaik%E2%80%99s%20indifference%20towards%20them%20as%20he%20preferred%20to%20deal%20with%20their%20central%20party%20leaders.%20Things%20came%20to%20a%20head%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%202008%20Kandhamal%20communal%20riots%2C%20which%20took%20a%20heavy%20toll%20on%20Patnaik%E2%80%99s%20secular%20image.%20Soon%20the%20chief%20minister%20realised%20that%20his%20alliance%20partner%20had%20become%20a%20liability%20and%20the%20coalition%20was%20becoming%20increasingly%20unsustainable.%20Though%20it%20is%20said%20that%20the%2011-year-old%20BJD-BJP%20alliance%20collapsed%20ahead%20of%20the%202009%20elections%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20seat%20sharing%2C%20it%20is%20an%20open%20secret%20that%20Patnaik%20had%20made%20up%20his%20mind%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20contested%20the%202009%20elections%20separately%20and%20the%20results%20made%20it%20more%20than%20obvious%20that%20all%20this%20time%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20been%20piggyback-riding%20on%20the%20BJD%20in%20Odisha.%20While%20the%20BJD%20came%20to%20power%20with%20a%20comfortable%20majority%2C%20the%20BJP%20could%20win%20just%20six%20seats%20in%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20147-strong%20assembly.%20It%20drew%20a%20blank%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20The%202014%20elections%20saw%20the%20saffron%20party%20bagging%2010%20assembly%20seats%20and%20the%20lone%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20of%20Sundergarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPatnaik%E2%80%99s%20changing%20face%20in%20the%20Modi%20years%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%202014%20marked%20a%20turning%20point%20in%20the%20relations%20between%20the%20BJD%20and%20BJP.%20With%20the%20BJP-led%20NDA%20coming%20to%20power%20at%20the%20Centre%20with%20a%20full%20majority%2C%20Patnaik%E2%80%99s%20relations%20with%20the%20central%20BJP%20leadership%2C%20especially%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20improved%20substantially.%20The%20chief%20minister%20realised%20the%20importance%20of%20having%20a%20friendly%20Centre%20to%20ensure%20the%20development%20of%20the%20state.%20Even%20though%20he%20followed%20an%20avowed%20policy%20of%20maintaining%20equidistance%20from%20the%20BJP%20and%20Congress%2C%20he%20supported%20the%20NDA%20government%20on%20several%20crucial%20issues%20inside%20the%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20the%20BJD%20backed%20the%20controversial%20Mines%20and%20Minerals%20(Development%20and%20Regulation)%20Amendment%20Bill%2C%202015%20and%20helped%20the%20NDA%20get%20it%20passed%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20where%20the%20BJP%20lacked%20the%20numbers.%20Patnaik%20was%20also%20among%20the%20first%20chief%20ministers%20of%20the%20country%20to%20welcome%20demonetisation%2C%20a%20move%20which%20faced%20criticism%20across%20the%20country.%20He%20also%20extended%20support%20to%20the%20controversial%20Goods%20and%20Services%20Tax%20(GST)%20when%20it%20was%20facing%20flak%20from%20several%20quarters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trend%20continued%20and%20by%20the%20time%20the%20next%20elections%20arrived%2C%20it%20was%20more%20or%20less%20clear%20that%20the%20policy%20of%20%E2%80%9Cequidistance%E2%80%9D%20was%20nothing%20but%20a%20fa%C3%A7ade%20which%20was%20becoming%20increasingly%20hard%20to%20defend.%20During%20NDA%E2%80%99s%20second%20term%20under%20Modi%2C%20the%20BJD%E2%80%99s%20support%20for%20the%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%20was%20even%20more%20obvious%2C%20with%20the%20party%20backing%20it%20on%20controversial%20issues%20like%20the%20scrapping%20of%20Article%20370%20and%20passage%20of%20the%20triple%20%3Cem%3Etalaq%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Bills.%20All%20this%20was%20done%20on%20the%20excuse%20of%20protecting%20either%20national%20interest%20or%20state%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20mutually%20convenient%20arrangement%2C%20with%20Patnaik%20getting%20generous%20financial%20assistance%20from%20the%20Centre%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20disastrous%20cyclones%20such%20as%20Fani%20which%20devastated%20a%20large%20part%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20coastal%20belt.%20The%20prime%20minister%2C%20too%2C%20found%20it%20convenient%20to%20cultivate%20regional%20satraps%20like%20Patnaik%20whose%20support%20he%20needed%20in%20the%20parliament%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20need%20being%20mutual%2C%20the%20bond%20between%20the%20two%20leaders%20soon%20became%20stronger%20and%20they%20refrained%20from%20criticising%20each%20other%20even%20at%20election%20rallies%2C%20though%20their%20parties%20happened%20to%20be%20rivals%20in%20state%20politics.%20This%20embarrassed%20the%20state%20BJP%20leaders%20no%20end%2C%20but%20the%20central%20party%20leadership%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20care%20less.%20The%20occasional%20attacks%20made%20on%20the%20Patnaik%20government%20by%20leaders%20like%20Amit%20Shah%20during%20their%20visits%20to%20the%20state%20appeared%20to%20be%20more%20for%20public%20consumption.%20Now%20even%20that%20has%20stopped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20elections%20around%20the%20corner%2C%20political%20expediency%20has%20once%20again%20taken%20precedence%20over%20principles%20and%20both%20the%20parties%20look%20almost%20set%20to%20join%20hands.%20While%20the%20BJP%20needs%20BJD%E2%80%99s%20support%20mainly%20to%20ensure%20that%20its%20Lok%20Sabha%20tally%20in%20the%20state%20goes%20up%2C%20which%20is%20crucial%20for%20the%20party%20to%20better%20its%202019%20record%20if%20not%20to%20actually%20realise%20the%20goal%20of%20400%20seats%2C%20the%20BJD%20is%20keen%20to%20retain%20its%20hold%20on%20the%20state%20so%20that%20Patnaik%20actualises%20the%20dream%20of%20becoming%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20the%20state%20for%20the%20sixth%20time%20in%20a%20row%2C%20a%20record%20in%20itself.%20If%20sources%20are%20to%20be%20believed%2C%20a%20tacit%20understanding%20between%20the%20top%20leadership%20of%20the%20two%20parties%20has%20been%20reached%20and%20seat%20sharing%20arrangement%20will%20be%20worked%20out%20accordingly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20both%20the%20parties%20out%20to%20defend%20their%20mutual%20interests%2C%20a%20marriage%20of%20convenience%20is%20once%20again%20on%20the%20cards.%20As%20political%20analyst%20Shashi%20Kant%20Mishra%20put%20it%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20could%20be%20embarrassing%20for%20the%20ordinary%20cadres%20of%20the%20two%20parties%20but%20their%20top%20leaders%20will%20be%20quite%20brazen%20about%20it.%20Jettisoning%20principles%20is%20a%20small%20sacrifice%20to%20make%20when%20bigger%20interests%20are%20involved.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fashutoshmishra%5C%22%3EAshutosh%20Mishra%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20an%20Odisha-based%20journalist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709869279000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F08091041%2FGH6wRL5W4AAQK0I.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fodisha-bjp-bjd-alliance%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20state%20BJP%20leaders%20are%20worried%20that%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJD%20may%20upset%20party%20cadres%2C%20the%20central%20leadership%20has%20decided%20that%20joining%20hands%20is%20the%20best%20way%20forward.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fodisha-bjp-bjd-alliance%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Canada%20mass%20stabbing%3A%206%20dead%2C%20student%20who%20lived%20with%20family%20arrested%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709867589000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108315537%2Cimgsize-1403798.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fcanada-mass-stabbing-6-dead-at-ottawa-student-who-lived-with-family-arrested%2Farticleshow%2F108315386.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108315386.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EA%2019-year-old%20stud