20the%20acting%20Taliban%20foreign%20minister%20Amir%20Khan%20Muttaqi%20in%20his%20office.%20He%20was%20accompanied%20by%20MEA%20officials%20as%20well%20as%20the%20head%20of%20the%20Indian%20technical%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20India%E2%80%99s%20non-recognition%20of%20the%20Taliban%20regime%2C%20its%20officials%20have%20maintained%20regular%20engagements%20with%20authorities%20in%20Kabul.%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20visit%20marks%20his%20fourth%20to%20Afghanistan%20since%20the%20fall%20of%20the%20Republic%20in%20August%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20statement%20from%20the%20Indian%20side%20about%20the%20talks.%20But%20the%20Taliban%20foreign%20ministry%20spokesperson%20tweeted%20that%20Singh%20conveyed%20to%20Muttaqi%20that%20India%20was%20%E2%80%9Cinterested%20in%20expand%5Bing%5D%20political%20%26amp%3B%20economic%20cooperation%20with%20Afghanistan%2C%20%26amp%3B%20enhancing%20trade%20via%20Chabahar%20port%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20Muttaqi%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Taliban%20government%20%E2%80%9Cseeks%20to%20strengthen%20political%20%26amp%3B%20economic%20relations%20with%20India%20as%20an%20important%20actor%20in%20the%20region%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20called%20on%20the%20Indian%20diplomat%20to%20%E2%80%9Cfacilitate%20visa%20issuance%20process%20for%20Afghan%20businessmen%2C%20patients%20%26amp%3B%20students%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FQaharBalkhi%2Fstatus%2F1765784719604510977%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Eas%20per%20the%20Taliban%20spokesperson%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20continues%20to%20maintain%20strict%20limitations%20on%20granting%20visas%20to%20Afghan%20nationals%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20Taliban%E2%80%99s%20resurgence%20to%20power%2C%20with%20no%20signs%20of%20relaxation%20thus%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20side%20also%20reportedly%20appreciated%20Taliban%20for%20%E2%80%9Censuring%20overall%20security%20%26amp%3B%20stability%E2%80%9D%2C%20as%20well%20as%20combating%20narcotics%20trade%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20India%20commended%20Taliban%20for%20bringing%20stability%2C%20Pakistan%20has%20called%20on%20the%20international%20community%20to%20put%20pressure%20on%20Kabul%20to%20terminate%20their%20relationship%20with%20the%20Tehreek-i-Taliban%20Pakistan%20(TTP).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1819821%2Fpakistan-urges-unsc-to-ask-afghan-taliban-to-cut-ties-with-ttp-eliminate-terrorism%5C%22%3ESpeaking%20at%20a%20special%20meeting%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council%20on%20Afghanistan%2C%20Pakistan%20claimed%20that%20the%20TTP%20could%20%E2%80%9Csoon%20pose%20a%20global%20terrorist%20threat%E2%80%9D%20if%20left%20unchecked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20diplomatic%20delegation%20had%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FKarzaiH%2Fstatus%2F1765685909222031402%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Ecalled%20on%3C%2Fa%3E%20former%20President%20Hamid%20Karzai%20at%20his%20residence%20in%20Kabul.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709866308000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F08082051%2FGIFTy40XoAAdASE.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fin-kabul-indian-diplomat-emphasises-economic-ties-amid-talibans-requests-for-visa-facilitation%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Despite%20India's%20non-recognition%20of%20the%20Taliban%20regime%2C%20its%20officials%20have%20maintained%20regular%20engagements%20with%20authorities%20in%20Kabul.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fin-kabul-indian-diplomat-emphasises-economic-ties-amid-talibans-requests-for-visa-facilitation%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Freedom%20and%20democracy%20'under%20attack%20at%20home%20and%20overseas'%3A%20Biden's%20State%20of%20the%20Union%20warning%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22p