rn%20price%20cap%2C%20and%20insisted%20on%20payment%20in%20yuan%2C%20dirham%20and%20US%20dollars%2C%20rather%20than%20Indian%20rupees%2C%20really%20point%20to%20%E2%80%98Russia%20never%20hurting%20India%E2%80%99%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20more%20importantly%2C%20what%20about%20the%20view%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20military%20that%20Russian%20deliveries%20of%20weapons%20and%20spare%20parts%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Findia%2Frussia-cannot-meet-arms-delivery-commitments-because-war-indian-air-force-says-2023-03-23%2F%5C%22%3Estalled%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%20That%20alone%20says%20that%20Russia%20is%20not%20India%E2%80%99s%20reliable%20friend.%20New%20Delhi%20is%20now%20looking%20to%20Western%20democracies%2C%20including%20France%20and%20the%20US%2C%20for%20arms%20and%20for%20collaboration%20in%20manufacturing%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20India%20%E2%80%93%20like%20China%20%E2%80%93%20has%20gained%20far%20more%20from%20economic%20and%20educational%20ties%20with%20Western%20democracies%20than%20with%20Russia.%20America%20buys%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftradingeconomics.com%2Findia%2Fexports-by-country%5C%22%3E18%25%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20exports%2C%20Russia%20a%20mere%200.66%25.%3C%2Fa%3E%20%C2%A0In%C2%A0%202022%2C%20there%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianembassy-moscow.gov.in%2Fpdf%2Frussia-fact-sheet-oct-2022.pdf%5C%22%3E30%2C%20000%3C%2Fa%3E%20Indians%20in%20Russia%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Farticle%2Feducation%2Fover-2-lakh-students-went-to-us-for-higher-studies-in-2021-22-report-122111401454_1.html%5C%22%3E200%2C000%20Indian%20%3Cem%3Estudents%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20the%20US%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinding%20its%20way%20through%20a%20maze%20of%20international%20interests%2C%20Ukraine%20could%20certainly%20tell%20some%20non-Western%20states%20that%20it%20is%20a%20victim%20of%20Russian%20imperialism%20and%20that%2C%20in%201991%2C%20when%20the%20Sovi