a.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fcoral-woman-2-1709730574-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fcoral-woman-2-1709730574-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fcoral-woman-2-1709730574-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-344106%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIn%202019%2C%20Uma%20was%20featured%20in%20an%20award-winning%20documentary%20titled%20%E2%80%98Coral%20Woman%E2%80%99.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20her%20efforts%20paid%20off%20and%20how!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20their%20award-winning%20documentary%20titled%20%E2%80%98Coral%20Woman%E2%80%99%20was%20released%2C%20featuring%20Uma%E2%80%99s%20journey%20to%20raise%20awareness%20of%20the%20damage%20being%20caused%20to%20marine%20life.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20India%2C%20we%20do%20not%20talk%20about%20the%20coral%20reefs%2C%20so%20this%20film%20was%20an%20eye-opener%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20Uma%20hosted%20several%20painting%20exhibitions%20across%20the%20country%20to%20draw%20interest%20to%20the%20subject.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20coral%20reefs%20in%20my%20paintings%20are%20not%20happy%20anymore.%20Today%2C%20I%20depict%20the%20walls%20of%20the%20ocean%20on%20my%20canvas%20and%20paint%20their%20sufferings.%20I%20believe%20art%20is%20a%20very%20powerful%20medium%20to%20bring%20about%20social%20transformation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20been%20a%20decade%20since%20her%20first%20dive%2C%20but%20Uma%20continues%20to%20raise%20awareness%20about%20marine%20pollution%20in%20schools%2C%20colleges%2C%20and%20corporate%20organisations.%20Recently%2C%20she%20was%20named%20the%20%E2%80%98Earth%20Champion%20of%20the%20Month%E2%80%99%20by%20Sony%20BBC%20Earth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPersonally%2C%20the%20transformation%20from%20being%20a%20homemaker%20to%20a%20sc